    1. https://widget.rentalcars.com (1)

      1. Content Security Policy (CSP) Header Not Set (1)
        1. GET https://widget.rentalcars.com/
          Alert tags
          • OWASP_2021_A05
          • OWASP_2017_A06
          Alert description

          Content Security Policy (CSP) is an added layer of security that helps to detect and mitigate certain types of attacks, including Cross Site Scripting (XSS) and data injection attacks. These attacks are used for everything from data theft to site defacement or distribution of malware. CSP provides a set of standard HTTP headers that allow website owners to declare approved sources of content that browsers should be allowed to load on that page — covered types are JavaScript, CSS, HTML frames, fonts, images and embeddable objects such as Java applets, ActiveX, audio and video files.

<script type="text/javascript" nonce="jlihcml4ukn80ab2ib4ackjug">
            
					function GAQPushTransition(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction) {
						serialiseEvent(new GAQEvent(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction));
					}

					function GAQPushSecureTransition(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction,domain) {
						serialiseSecureEvent(new GAQEvent(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction),domain);
					}

					function GAQPush(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction) {
						pushEvent(new GAQEvent(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction));
					}

					function GAQPushPage(gaq_event_name, action){
						pushPageEvent(new GAQPageEvent(gaq_event_name, action));
					}

					function GAQPushLinkByPost(form) {
						try {
							pushLinkByPostEvent(new GAQLinkByPostEvent(form));
						} catch(err) {
						}
					}

					$(document).ready(function() {
						try {
							if ('/LoadingSearchResults.do' !== window.location.pathname) {
								$(deserialiseEvents(true)).each(function() {
									pushEvent(this);
								});
							}
						} catch (err) {

						}
					});

					var cookie_name = 'gaw_track';

					var accountPrefixes = new Array();
					accountPrefixes.push('m');

					function serialiseEvent(gaq_event) {
						var eventList = deserialiseEvents(false);
						if (!isDuplicateGAEvent(eventList, gaq_event)) {
							eventList.push(gaq_event);
						}
						if ('' === 'true' && '' === 'true') {
							$.cookies.set(cookie_name, $.toJSON(eventList));
						}
					}

					function serialiseSecureEvent(gaq_event,domain) {
						ajaxSetCookie({
							name: cookie_name,
							value: $.toJSON(gaq_event),
							domain: domain
						});
					}

					function deserialiseEvents(deleteAfterRead) {
						var events = new Array();

						if ($.cookies.get(cookie_name) !== null) {
							var json = $.evalJSON($.toJSON($.cookies.get(cookie_name)));

							if (json instanceof Array) {
								$(json).each(function() {
									events.push(new GAQEvent(this.gaq_event_name, this.category, this.action, this.label, this.value, this.non_interaction));
								});
							}
							else {
								events.push(new GAQEvent(json.gaq_event_name, json.category, json.action, json.label, json.value, json.non_interaction));
							}
						}

						if (deleteAfterRead) {
							$.cookies.set(cookie_name, null);
						}

						return events;
					}

					function pushEvent(event) {
						try{
							_gaq.push([event.gaq_event_name, event.category, event.action, event.label, event.value, event.non_interaction]);
							for (var i = 0; i < accountPrefixes.length; i++) {
								var prefix = accountPrefixes[i];
								_gaq.push([prefix + '.' + event.gaq_event_name, event.category, event.action, event.label, event.value, event.non_interaction]);
							}
						} catch(error){
							window.console.error('Could not push to Google Analytics because: \n', error);
						}
					}

					function pushPageEvent(e) {
						try{
							_gaq.push([e.gaq_event_name, e.action]);
							for (var i = 0; i < accountPrefixes.length; i++) {
								var prefix = accountPrefixes[i];
								_gaq.push([prefix + '.' + e.gaq_event_name, e.action]);
							}
						}catch(err){

						}
					}

					function pushLinkByPostEvent(e) {
						_gaq.push([e.gaq_event_name, e.form]);
						for (var i = 0; i < accountPrefixes.length; i++) {
							var prefix = accountPrefixes[i];
							_gaq.push([prefix + '.' + e.gaq_event_name, e.form]);
						}
					}


					/*
					 * Transition management
					 * Make sure duplicate events are not tracker on page transition
					 */
					function isDuplicateGAEvent(existingEvents, newEvent) {
						var key = newEvent.category + '#' + newEvent.action + '#' + newEvent.label;
						var found = false;
						for (var i = 0; i < existingEvents.length; i++) {
							var existingEventsKey = existingEvents[i].category + '#' + existingEvents[i].action + '#' + existingEvents[i].label;
							if (existingEventsKey === key) {
								found = true;
								break;
							}
						}
						return found;
					}


					/**
					 * Object representation of the Google Analytics _gaq.push(...) method
					 * https://developers.google.com/analytics/devguides/collection/gajs/eventTrackerGuide
					 */
					function GAQEvent(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction) {
						this.gaq_event_name = gaq_event_name;
						this.category = category;
						this.action = action;
						this.label = label;
						this.value = value;
						this.non_interaction = non_interaction;
					}

					function GAQPageEvent(gaq_event_name, action) {
						this.gaq_event_name = gaq_event_name;
						this.action = action;
					}

					function GAQLinkByPostEvent(form) {
						this.gaq_event_name = '_linkByPost';
						this.form = form;
					}
				</script>

                                    $(document).ready(function(){
                                           var lcf = document.getElementById('langCurrencyForm');
                                           $('#alternative-languages a').bind('click',function(e){
                                               e.preventDefault();
                                               lcf['langCurrencyActionType'].value='language';
                                               lcf['preflang'].value=$(this).attr("id");
											   lcf['lang'].value=$(this).attr("id");
                                               try {
                                                  	GAQPushTransition('_trackEvent', 'LangChange', '361', $(this).attr("id"), 1, true);
                                                  } catch (e) {}
                                               lcf.submit();
                                           });
                                    });
                                </script>

<script type="text/javascript" nonce="jlihcml4ukn80ab2ib4ackjug">
       	function formSubmit()
		{
	    if( $('#show_return').attr('checked') == true ) {
            showReturnDropDown();
        }

		$('input[name=locationName]').val( $( droplists[2].jqSelector ).find('option:selected').html() );
        $('input[name=dropLocationName]').val( $( droplists[5].jqSelector ).find('option:selected').html() );
        
        if( $( droplists[2].jqSelector ).val() == -1 && $( droplists[5].jqSelector ).val() == -1 ) {
            
            if( $( droplists[0].jqSelector ).val() == $( droplists[3].jqSelector ).val() && $( droplists[1].jqSelector ).val() == $( droplists[4].jqSelector ).val() ) {
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=searchType]').val('allareasgeosearch');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=doFiltering]').val('true');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterTo]').val('20');
            } else {                          
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=searchType]').val('manytomanysearch');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=doFiltering]').val('true');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterTo]').val('20');
            }
    
        } else if(  $( droplists[2].jqSelector ).val() == -1 && $( droplists[5].jqSelector ).val() != -1 ) {
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=searchType]').val('manytoonesearch');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=doFiltering]').val('true');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterTo]').val('20');
        } else if(  $( droplists[2].jqSelector ).val() != -1 && $( droplists[5].jqSelector ).val() == -1 ) {
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=searchType]').val('onetomanysearch');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=doFiltering]').val('true');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterTo]').val('20');
        } else {
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=searchType]').val('');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=doFiltering]').val('false');
        	$('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterTo]').val('1000');
        }
       

		if(validateSearchResultsForm( document.SearchResultsForm ) ) {			
			saveInput();
			$('form[name=SearchResultsForm]').append(
                    $( document.createElement('input') )
                        .attr('type','hidden')
                        .attr('name','fromLocChoose')
                        .val(true)
                );
			$('form[name=SearchResultsForm]').submit();      
		}else {
			return false;
		}
	}
	
	 function droplistPopulate( data, droplistJSON, callback ) {
        $.ajax({
            url: '/AjaxDroplists.do',
            data: data + '&wrapNonAirports=true',
            dataType: 'json',
            success: function( result ) {            
                $( droplists ).each( function() {                 
                    if( this.index >= droplistJSON.index ) {                  
                        var element = $( this.jqSelector ).empty().append( $( document.createElement('option') ).html( pleaseSelectTxt ).val( 0 ) );                                      
                    }
                    if( this.index != droplistJSON.index )
                        $( element ).attr('disabled',true);
                });
                
                $( result ).each(function() {                 
                    
                    if( typeof this.timeZone != 'undefined' ) {
                        
                        $( droplistJSON.jqSelector ).append( 
                                $( document.createElement('option') )
                                    .html( this.name )
                                    .attr('timeZone',this.timeZone)
                                    .val( this.id ) )
                                .attr('disabled',false);
                    } else {
                        
                        $( droplistJSON.jqSelector ).append( 
                                $( document.createElement('option') )
                                    .html( this.name )
                                    .val( this.id ) )
                                .attr('disabled',false);                      
                    }   
                });
                if( typeof callback != 'undefined' ) callback.call(); 
            }
        });
    }   
	
	function droplistPopulateWithData( data ) {
        $.ajax({
            url: '/AjaxDroplists.do',
            data: data + '&mode=fillAll&wrapNonAirports=true',
            dataType: 'json',
            success: function( result ) {   
                $( droplists ).each(function() {                  
                    var selector = this.jqSelector;
                    var enable = false;         
                        $( selector ).empty().append( $( document.createElement('option') ).html( pleaseSelectTxt ).val( 0 ) ).attr('disabled',true);
                        
                        if (typeof(this)=='object' ) {
	                        $( result[ this.fillAllName ] ).each(function() {
	                            
	                            if( typeof this.timeZone != 'undefined' ) {
	                                
	                                $( selector ).append(
	                                        $( document.createElement('option') )
	                                            .html( this.name )
	                                            .attr('timeZone',this.timeZone)
	                                            .val( this.id )
	                                    ); 
	                                    enable = true;
	                                
	                            } else {
	                                
	                                $( selector ).append(
	                                        $( document.createElement('option') )
	                                            .html( this.name )
	                                            .val( this.id )
	                                    ); 
	                                    enable = true;                              
	                            }
	                            
	                        });  
                        }
                  
                        if( enable == true ) $( selector ).attr('disabled', false);
                        if( typeof result[ this.fillAllSelect ] != 'undefined' && result[ this.fillAllSelect ] != ''  ) {
                            $( selector ).val( result[ this.fillAllSelect ] ).find('option[value=0]').attr('disabled',true);                    
                        }                   
                });
            }
        });
    }

</script>

<script type="text/javascript" nonce="<tju:cspInlineNonce />">
    $(function() {
        $('fieldset.datetime').after(
            $( document.createElement('div') )
                .addClass('time-msg')
                .append( $( document.createElement('span') )  )
                .append( 
                    $( document.createElement('div') )
                        .addClass('time-msg-arrow')
                )
        );
        
        $('select[name=puHour], select[name=doHour], select[name=puMinute], select[name=doMinute]').change(function() {
            getHourDiff(
                $('select[name=puHour]').val(), 
                $('select[name=puMinute]').val(),
                $('select[name=doHour]').val(),
                $('select[name=doMinute]').val()
            );
        });
    });
    
    function getHourDiff(puHour, puMinute, doHour, doMinute) {      
        var puMinutes = -1;
        var doMinutes = -1;     
        try {
            puMinutes = (parseInt(puHour)*60) + parseInt(puMinute);
            doMinutes = (parseInt(doHour)*60) + parseInt(doMinute);
        } catch (e) {}
        $('.time-msg').hide();
        $('.time-msg span').html('');
        
        if(!isNaN(puMinutes)&&!isNaN(doMinutes)&&puMinutes!=-1&&doMinutes!=-1&&getPuDate().getTime()!=getDoDate().getTime()){
            var difference = doMinutes-puMinutes;
            if(difference>0&&difference<=60) {
                $('.time-msg span').html('<tju:javascriptescape>You can save a full days car rental price by reducing your rental duration by 1 hour</tju:javascriptescape>');
                $('.time-msg').show();
            } else if(difference>60&&difference<=120) {
                $('.time-msg span').html('<tju:javascriptescape>You can save a full days car rental price by reducing your rental duration by 2 hour</tju:javascriptescape>');
                $('.time-msg').show();
            } else if(difference>120&&difference<=180) {
                $('.time-msg span').html('<tju:javascriptescape>You can save a full days car rental price by reducing your rental duration by 3 hour</tju:javascriptescape>');
                $('.time-msg').show();
            }
        }       
    }

    (function() {

        function _getUtmzCookieValue() {

                    return utmzCookieValues;
                }
                else {
                    utmzCookieValues = {};
                    return utmzCookieValues;
                }
            }
        }

            return (typeof(val) !== 'undefined' ? val : '');
        }

<script type="text/javascript" nonce="jlihcml4ukn80ab2ib4ackjug">
                function tagSrcIncludesPathSubstring(tag, substringTerms) {
                    var tagIncludesSubstring = false;
                    $.each(substringTerms, function(index, term) {
                        if (typeof tag.src != undefined && tag.src.indexOf(term) !== -1) {
                            tagIncludesSubstring = true;
                            return false; // breaks $.each loop
                        }
                    });

                    return tagIncludesSubstring;
                }

                function getGoogleMapCountFromTags(tags) {
                    var cnCountryOfResidence = false;
                    var googleMapUrls = cnCountryOfResidence ? ['maps.google.cn'] : ['maps.googleapis.com', 'maps.google.com'];

                    var googleMapCount = 0;
                    $.each(tags, function(index, tag) {
                        if (tagSrcIncludesPathSubstring(tag, googleMapUrls)) {
                            googleMapCount++;
                        }
                    });
                    return googleMapCount;
                }

                $(document).ready(function() {
                    var scriptTags = document.scripts;
                    var imgTags = document.images;

                    var googleMapCount = getGoogleMapCountFromTags(scriptTags);
                    var staticGoogleMapCount = getGoogleMapCountFromTags(imgTags);

                    GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'ErrorDebugInfo', 'GoogleMapScriptCount', 'PN:lp-default:'+googleMapCount, 1, true);
                    GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'ErrorDebugInfo', 'StaticGoogleMapImageCount', 'PN:lp-default:'+staticGoogleMapCount, 1, true);
                });

    	random = Math.floor(Math.random() * 3);

    	else
    		group = 'C';

    }

          Solution

          Ensure that your web server, application server, load balancer, etc. is configured to set the Content-Security-Policy header.

  2. Risk=Medium, Confidence=Medium (3)

    1. https://cdn.cookielaw.org (1)

      1. Cross-Domain Misconfiguration (1)
        1. GET https://cdn.cookielaw.org/scripttemplates/otSDKStub.js
          Alert tags
          • OWASP_2021_A01
          • OWASP_2017_A05
          Alert description

          Web browser data loading may be possible, due to a Cross Origin Resource Sharing (CORS) misconfiguration on the web server
          Other info

          The CORS misconfiguration on the web server permits cross-domain read requests from arbitrary third party domains, using unauthenticated APIs on this domain. Web browser implementations do not permit arbitrary third parties to read the response from authenticated APIs, however. This reduces the risk somewhat. This misconfiguration could be used by an attacker to access data that is available in an unauthenticated manner, but which uses some other form of security, such as IP address white-listing.

					var cookie_name = 'gaw_track';

					var accountPrefixes = new Array();
					accountPrefixes.push('m');

					function serialiseEvent(gaq_event) {
						var eventList = deserialiseEvents(false);
						if (!isDuplicateGAEvent(eventList, gaq_event)) {
							eventList.push(gaq_event);
						}
						if ('' === 'true' && '' === 'true') {
							$.cookies.set(cookie_name, $.toJSON(eventList));
						}
					}

					function serialiseSecureEvent(gaq_event,domain) {
						ajaxSetCookie({
							name: cookie_name,
							value: $.toJSON(gaq_event),
							domain: domain
						});
					}

					function deserialiseEvents(deleteAfterRead) {
						var events = new Array();

						if ($.cookies.get(cookie_name) !== null) {
							var json = $.evalJSON($.toJSON($.cookies.get(cookie_name)));

							if (json instanceof Array) {
								$(json).each(function() {
									events.push(new GAQEvent(this.gaq_event_name, this.category, this.action, this.label, this.value, this.non_interaction));
								});
							}
							else {
								events.push(new GAQEvent(json.gaq_event_name, json.category, json.action, json.label, json.value, json.non_interaction));
							}
						}

						if (deleteAfterRead) {
							$.cookies.set(cookie_name, null);
						}

						return events;
					}

					function pushEvent(event) {
						try{
							_gaq.push([event.gaq_event_name, event.category, event.action, event.label, event.value, event.non_interaction]);
							for (var i = 0; i < accountPrefixes.length; i++) {
								var prefix = accountPrefixes[i];
								_gaq.push([prefix + '.' + event.gaq_event_name, event.category, event.action, event.label, event.value, event.non_interaction]);
							}
						} catch(error){
							window.console.error('Could not push to Google Analytics because: \n', error);
						}
					}

					function pushPageEvent(e) {
						try{
							_gaq.push([e.gaq_event_name, e.action]);
							for (var i = 0; i < accountPrefixes.length; i++) {
								var prefix = accountPrefixes[i];
								_gaq.push([prefix + '.' + e.gaq_event_name, e.action]);
							}
						}catch(err){

						}
					}

					function pushLinkByPostEvent(e) {
						_gaq.push([e.gaq_event_name, e.form]);
						for (var i = 0; i < accountPrefixes.length; i++) {
							var prefix = accountPrefixes[i];
							_gaq.push([prefix + '.' + e.gaq_event_name, e.form]);
						}
					}


					/*
					 * Transition management
					 * Make sure duplicate events are not tracker on page transition
					 */
					function isDuplicateGAEvent(existingEvents, newEvent) {
						var key = newEvent.category + '#' + newEvent.action + '#' + newEvent.label;
						var found = false;
						for (var i = 0; i < existingEvents.length; i++) {
							var existingEventsKey = existingEvents[i].category + '#' + existingEvents[i].action + '#' + existingEvents[i].label;
							if (existingEventsKey === key) {
								found = true;
								break;
							}
						}
						return found;
					}


					/**
					 * Object representation of the Google Analytics _gaq.push(...) method
					 * https://developers.google.com/analytics/devguides/collection/gajs/eventTrackerGuide
					 */
					function GAQEvent(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction) {
						this.gaq_event_name = gaq_event_name;
						this.category = category;
						this.action = action;
						this.label = label;
						this.value = value;
						this.non_interaction = non_interaction;
					}

					function GAQPageEvent(gaq_event_name, action) {
						this.gaq_event_name = gaq_event_name;
						this.action = action;
					}

					function GAQLinkByPostEvent(form) {
						this.gaq_event_name = '_linkByPost';
						this.form = form;
					}

<script nonce="jlihcml4ukn80ab2ib4ackjug">
                                    $(document).ready(function(){
                                           var lcf = document.getElementById('langCurrencyForm');
                                           $('#alternative-languages a').bind('click',function(e){
                                               e.preventDefault();
                                               lcf['langCurrencyActionType'].value='language';
                                               lcf['preflang'].value=$(this).attr("id");
											   lcf['lang'].value=$(this).attr("id");
                                               try {
                                                  	GAQPushTransition('_trackEvent', 'LangChange', '361', $(this).attr("id"), 1, true);
                                                  } catch (e) {}
                                               lcf.submit();
                                           });
                                    });
                                </script>

<script type="text/javascript" nonce="jlihcml4ukn80ab2ib4ackjug">
       	function formSubmit()
		{
	    if( $('#show_return').attr('checked') == true ) {
            showReturnDropDown();
        }

		$('input[name=locationName]').val( $( droplists[2].jqSelector ).find('option:selected').html() );
        $('input[name=dropLocationName]').val( $( droplists[5].jqSelector ).find('option:selected').html() );
        
        if( $( droplists[2].jqSelector ).val() == -1 && $( droplists[5].jqSelector ).val() == -1 ) {
            
            if( $( droplists[0].jqSelector ).val() == $( droplists[3].jqSelector ).val() && $( droplists[1].jqSelector ).val() == $( droplists[4].jqSelector ).val() ) {
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=searchType]').val('allareasgeosearch');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=doFiltering]').val('true');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterTo]').val('20');
            } else {                          
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=searchType]').val('manytomanysearch');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=doFiltering]').val('true');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterTo]').val('20');
            }
    
        } else if(  $( droplists[2].jqSelector ).val() == -1 && $( droplists[5].jqSelector ).val() != -1 ) {
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=searchType]').val('manytoonesearch');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=doFiltering]').val('true');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterTo]').val('20');
        } else if(  $( droplists[2].jqSelector ).val() != -1 && $( droplists[5].jqSelector ).val() == -1 ) {
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=searchType]').val('onetomanysearch');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=doFiltering]').val('true');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterTo]').val('20');
        } else {
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=searchType]').val('');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=doFiltering]').val('false');
        	$('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterTo]').val('1000');
        }
       

		if(validateSearchResultsForm( document.SearchResultsForm ) ) {			
			saveInput();
			$('form[name=SearchResultsForm]').append(
                    $( document.createElement('input') )
                        .attr('type','hidden')
                        .attr('name','fromLocChoose')
                        .val(true)
                );
			$('form[name=SearchResultsForm]').submit();      
		}else {
			return false;
		}
	}
	
	 function droplistPopulate( data, droplistJSON, callback ) {
        $.ajax({
            url: '/AjaxDroplists.do',
            data: data + '&wrapNonAirports=true',
            dataType: 'json',
            success: function( result ) {            
                $( droplists ).each( function() {                 
                    if( this.index >= droplistJSON.index ) {                  
                        var element = $( this.jqSelector ).empty().append( $( document.createElement('option') ).html( pleaseSelectTxt ).val( 0 ) );                                      
                    }
                    if( this.index != droplistJSON.index )
                        $( element ).attr('disabled',true);
                });
                
                $( result ).each(function() {                 
                    
                    if( typeof this.timeZone != 'undefined' ) {
                        
                        $( droplistJSON.jqSelector ).append( 
                                $( document.createElement('option') )
                                    .html( this.name )
                                    .attr('timeZone',this.timeZone)
                                    .val( this.id ) )
                                .attr('disabled',false);
                    } else {
                        
                        $( droplistJSON.jqSelector ).append( 
                                $( document.createElement('option') )
                                    .html( this.name )
                                    .val( this.id ) )
                                .attr('disabled',false);                      
                    }   
                });
                if( typeof callback != 'undefined' ) callback.call(); 
            }
        });
    }   
	
	function droplistPopulateWithData( data ) {
        $.ajax({
            url: '/AjaxDroplists.do',
            data: data + '&mode=fillAll&wrapNonAirports=true',
            dataType: 'json',
            success: function( result ) {   
                $( droplists ).each(function() {                  
                    var selector = this.jqSelector;
                    var enable = false;         
                        $( selector ).empty().append( $( document.createElement('option') ).html( pleaseSelectTxt ).val( 0 ) ).attr('disabled',true);
                        
                        if (typeof(this)=='object' ) {
	                        $( result[ this.fillAllName ] ).each(function() {
	                            
	                            if( typeof this.timeZone != 'undefined' ) {
	                                
	                                $( selector ).append(
	                                        $( document.createElement('option') )
	                                            .html( this.name )
	                                            .attr('timeZone',this.timeZone)
	                                            .val( this.id )
	                                    ); 
	                                    enable = true;
	                                
	                            } else {
	                                
	                                $( selector ).append(
	                                        $( document.createElement('option') )
	                                            .html( this.name )
	                                            .val( this.id )
	                                    ); 
	                                    enable = true;                              
	                            }
	                            
	                        });  
                        }
                  
                        if( enable == true ) $( selector ).attr('disabled', false);
                        if( typeof result[ this.fillAllSelect ] != 'undefined' && result[ this.fillAllSelect ] != ''  ) {
                            $( selector ).val( result[ this.fillAllSelect ] ).find('option[value=0]').attr('disabled',true);                    
                        }                   
                });
            }
        });
    }

</script>

<script type="text/javascript" nonce="<tju:cspInlineNonce />">
    $(function() {
        $('fieldset.datetime').after(
            $( document.createElement('div') )
                .addClass('time-msg')
                .append( $( document.createElement('span') )  )
                .append( 
                    $( document.createElement('div') )
                        .addClass('time-msg-arrow')
                )
        );
        
        $('select[name=puHour], select[name=doHour], select[name=puMinute], select[name=doMinute]').change(function() {
            getHourDiff(
                $('select[name=puHour]').val(), 
                $('select[name=puMinute]').val(),
                $('select[name=doHour]').val(),
                $('select[name=doMinute]').val()
            );
        });
    });
    
    function getHourDiff(puHour, puMinute, doHour, doMinute) {      
        var puMinutes = -1;
        var doMinutes = -1;     
        try {
            puMinutes = (parseInt(puHour)*60) + parseInt(puMinute);
            doMinutes = (parseInt(doHour)*60) + parseInt(doMinute);
        } catch (e) {}
        $('.time-msg').hide();
        $('.time-msg span').html('');
        
        if(!isNaN(puMinutes)&&!isNaN(doMinutes)&&puMinutes!=-1&&doMinutes!=-1&&getPuDate().getTime()!=getDoDate().getTime()){
            var difference = doMinutes-puMinutes;
            if(difference>0&&difference<=60) {
                $('.time-msg span').html('<tju:javascriptescape>You can save a full days car rental price by reducing your rental duration by 1 hour</tju:javascriptescape>');
                $('.time-msg').show();
            } else if(difference>60&&difference<=120) {
                $('.time-msg span').html('<tju:javascriptescape>You can save a full days car rental price by reducing your rental duration by 2 hour</tju:javascriptescape>');
                $('.time-msg').show();
            } else if(difference>120&&difference<=180) {
                $('.time-msg span').html('<tju:javascriptescape>You can save a full days car rental price by reducing your rental duration by 3 hour</tju:javascriptescape>');
                $('.time-msg').show();
            }
        }       
    }

</script><fieldset id="driveragefieldset">

    /* UtmzUtils */
    (function() {

        var utmzCookieValues = null;

        function _getUtmzCookieValue() {
            var val = (document.cookie.match(/^(?:.*;)?\s__utmz=([^;]+)(?:.*)?$/)||[,null])[1];
            return val;
        }

        function _getUtmzCookieValues() {
            if (utmzCookieValues !== null) {
                return utmzCookieValues;
            }
            else {
                var utmzCookieValue = _getUtmzCookieValue();
                if (utmzCookieValue !== null) {
                    var pairs = utmzCookieValue.split('.').slice(4).join('.').split('|');
                    var ga = {};
                    for (var i = 0; i < pairs.length; i++) {
                        var temp = pairs[i].split('=');
                        ga[temp[0]] = temp[1];
                    }
                    utmzCookieValues = ga;
                    return utmzCookieValues;
                }
                else {
                    utmzCookieValues = {};
                    return utmzCookieValues;
                }
            }
        }

        function getValue(name) {
            var val = _getUtmzCookieValues()[name];
            return (typeof(val) !== 'undefined' ? val : '');
        }

        window.UtmzUtils = {
            getValue: getValue,
            _getUtmzCookieValue: _getUtmzCookieValue,
            _getUtmzCookieValues: _getUtmzCookieValues
        };

    })();
</script>

<script type="text/javascript" nonce="jlihcml4ukn80ab2ib4ackjug">
                function tagSrcIncludesPathSubstring(tag, substringTerms) {
                    var tagIncludesSubstring = false;
                    $.each(substringTerms, function(index, term) {
                        if (typeof tag.src != undefined && tag.src.indexOf(term) !== -1) {
                            tagIncludesSubstring = true;
                            return false; // breaks $.each loop
                        }
                    });

                    return tagIncludesSubstring;
                }

                function getGoogleMapCountFromTags(tags) {
                    var cnCountryOfResidence = false;
                    var googleMapUrls = cnCountryOfResidence ? ['maps.google.cn'] : ['maps.googleapis.com', 'maps.google.com'];

                    var googleMapCount = 0;
                    $.each(tags, function(index, tag) {
                        if (tagSrcIncludesPathSubstring(tag, googleMapUrls)) {
                            googleMapCount++;
                        }
                    });
                    return googleMapCount;
                }

                $(document).ready(function() {
                    var scriptTags = document.scripts;
                    var imgTags = document.images;

                    var googleMapCount = getGoogleMapCountFromTags(scriptTags);
                    var staticGoogleMapCount = getGoogleMapCountFromTags(imgTags);

                    GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'ErrorDebugInfo', 'GoogleMapScriptCount', 'PN:lp-default:'+googleMapCount, 1, true);
                    GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'ErrorDebugInfo', 'StaticGoogleMapImageCount', 'PN:lp-default:'+staticGoogleMapCount, 1, true);
                });

          Parameter 
          x-frame-options
          Solution

          Modern Web browsers support the Content-Security-Policy and X-Frame-Options HTTP headers. Ensure one of them is set on all web pages returned by your site/app.

          If you expect the page to be framed only by pages on your server (e.g. it's part of a FRAMESET) then you'll want to use SAMEORIGIN, otherwise if you never expect the page to be framed, you should use DENY. Alternatively consider implementing Content Security Policy's "frame-ancestors" directive.

      1. Absence of Anti-CSRF Tokens (1)

          Alert tags
          • OWASP_2021_A01
          • WSTG-v42-SESS-05
          • OWASP_2017_A05
          Alert description

          No Anti-CSRF tokens were found in a HTML submission form.

          A cross-site request forgery is an attack that involves forcing a victim to send an HTTP request to a target destination without their knowledge or intent in order to perform an action as the victim. The underlying cause is application functionality using predictable URL/form actions in a repeatable way. The nature of the attack is that CSRF exploits the trust that a web site has for a user. By contrast, cross-site scripting (XSS) exploits the trust that a user has for a web site. Like XSS, CSRF attacks are not necessarily cross-site, but they can be. Cross-site request forgery is also known as CSRF, XSRF, one-click attack, session riding, confused deputy, and sea surf.

          CSRF attacks are effective in a number of situations, including:

          * The victim has an active session on the target site.

          * The victim is authenticated via HTTP auth on the target site.

          * The victim is on the same local network as the target site.

          CSRF has primarily been used to perform an action against a target site using the victim's privileges, but recent techniques have been discovered to disclose information by gaining access to the response. The risk of information disclosure is dramatically increased when the target site is vulnerable to XSS, because XSS can be used as a platform for CSRF, allowing the attack to operate within the bounds of the same-origin policy.
          Other info

          No known Anti-CSRF token [anticsrf, CSRFToken, __RequestVerificationToken, csrfmiddlewaretoken, authenticity_token, OWASP_CSRFTOKEN, anoncsrf, csrf_token, _csrf, _csrfSecret, __csrf_magic, CSRF, _token, _csrf_token] was found in the following HTML form: [Form 1: "city" "country" "crmActionType" "crmCreateEmail" "crmCreatePsw" "crmEmail" "crmOrigin" "crmPsw" "dropCity" "dropCountry" "dropLocation" "dropLocationName" "email" "lang" "langCurrencyActionType" "location" "locationName" "prefcurrency" "preflang" "tmp_email" "tmp_ref" ].

					var cookie_name = 'gaw_track';

					var accountPrefixes = new Array();
					accountPrefixes.push('m');

					function serialiseEvent(gaq_event) {
						var eventList = deserialiseEvents(false);
						if (!isDuplicateGAEvent(eventList, gaq_event)) {
							eventList.push(gaq_event);
						}
						if ('' === 'true' && '' === 'true') {
							$.cookies.set(cookie_name, $.toJSON(eventList));
						}
					}

					function serialiseSecureEvent(gaq_event,domain) {
						ajaxSetCookie({
							name: cookie_name,
							value: $.toJSON(gaq_event),
							domain: domain
						});
					}

					function deserialiseEvents(deleteAfterRead) {
						var events = new Array();

						if ($.cookies.get(cookie_name) !== null) {
							var json = $.evalJSON($.toJSON($.cookies.get(cookie_name)));

							if (json instanceof Array) {
								$(json).each(function() {
									events.push(new GAQEvent(this.gaq_event_name, this.category, this.action, this.label, this.value, this.non_interaction));
								});
							}
							else {
								events.push(new GAQEvent(json.gaq_event_name, json.category, json.action, json.label, json.value, json.non_interaction));
							}
						}

						if (deleteAfterRead) {
							$.cookies.set(cookie_name, null);
						}

						return events;
					}

					function pushEvent(event) {
						try{
							_gaq.push([event.gaq_event_name, event.category, event.action, event.label, event.value, event.non_interaction]);
							for (var i = 0; i < accountPrefixes.length; i++) {
								var prefix = accountPrefixes[i];
								_gaq.push([prefix + '.' + event.gaq_event_name, event.category, event.action, event.label, event.value, event.non_interaction]);
							}
						} catch(error){
							window.console.error('Could not push to Google Analytics because: \n', error);
						}
					}

					function pushPageEvent(e) {
						try{
							_gaq.push([e.gaq_event_name, e.action]);
							for (var i = 0; i < accountPrefixes.length; i++) {
								var prefix = accountPrefixes[i];
								_gaq.push([prefix + '.' + e.gaq_event_name, e.action]);
							}
						}catch(err){

						}
					}

					function pushLinkByPostEvent(e) {
						_gaq.push([e.gaq_event_name, e.form]);
						for (var i = 0; i < accountPrefixes.length; i++) {
							var prefix = accountPrefixes[i];
							_gaq.push([prefix + '.' + e.gaq_event_name, e.form]);
						}
					}


					/*
					 * Transition management
					 * Make sure duplicate events are not tracker on page transition
					 */
					function isDuplicateGAEvent(existingEvents, newEvent) {
						var key = newEvent.category + '#' + newEvent.action + '#' + newEvent.label;
						var found = false;
						for (var i = 0; i < existingEvents.length; i++) {
							var existingEventsKey = existingEvents[i].category + '#' + existingEvents[i].action + '#' + existingEvents[i].label;
							if (existingEventsKey === key) {
								found = true;
								break;
							}
						}
						return found;
					}


					/**
					 * Object representation of the Google Analytics _gaq.push(...) method
					 * https://developers.google.com/analytics/devguides/collection/gajs/eventTrackerGuide
					 */
					function GAQEvent(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction) {
						this.gaq_event_name = gaq_event_name;
						this.category = category;
						this.action = action;
						this.label = label;
						this.value = value;
						this.non_interaction = non_interaction;
					}

					function GAQPageEvent(gaq_event_name, action) {
						this.gaq_event_name = gaq_event_name;
						this.action = action;
					}

					function GAQLinkByPostEvent(form) {
						this.gaq_event_name = '_linkByPost';
						this.form = form;
					}
				</script>

<script type="text/javascript" nonce="jlihcml4ukn80ab2ib4ackjug">
       	function formSubmit()
		{
	    if( $('#show_return').attr('checked') == true ) {
            showReturnDropDown();
        }

		$('input[name=locationName]').val( $( droplists[2].jqSelector ).find('option:selected').html() );
        $('input[name=dropLocationName]').val( $( droplists[5].jqSelector ).find('option:selected').html() );
        
        if( $( droplists[2].jqSelector ).val() == -1 && $( droplists[5].jqSelector ).val() == -1 ) {
            
            if( $( droplists[0].jqSelector ).val() == $( droplists[3].jqSelector ).val() && $( droplists[1].jqSelector ).val() == $( droplists[4].jqSelector ).val() ) {
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=searchType]').val('allareasgeosearch');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=doFiltering]').val('true');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterTo]').val('20');
            } else {                          
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=searchType]').val('manytomanysearch');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=doFiltering]').val('true');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterTo]').val('20');
            }
    
        } else if(  $( droplists[2].jqSelector ).val() == -1 && $( droplists[5].jqSelector ).val() != -1 ) {
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=searchType]').val('manytoonesearch');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=doFiltering]').val('true');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterTo]').val('20');
        } else if(  $( droplists[2].jqSelector ).val() != -1 && $( droplists[5].jqSelector ).val() == -1 ) {
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=searchType]').val('onetomanysearch');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=doFiltering]').val('true');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterTo]').val('20');
        } else {
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=searchType]').val('');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=doFiltering]').val('false');
        	$('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterTo]').val('1000');
        }
       

		if(validateSearchResultsForm( document.SearchResultsForm ) ) {			
			saveInput();
			$('form[name=SearchResultsForm]').append(
                    $( document.createElement('input') )
                        .attr('type','hidden')
                        .attr('name','fromLocChoose')
                        .val(true)
                );
			$('form[name=SearchResultsForm]').submit();      
		}else {
			return false;
		}
	}
	
	 function droplistPopulate( data, droplistJSON, callback ) {
        $.ajax({
            url: '/AjaxDroplists.do',
            data: data + '&wrapNonAirports=true',
            dataType: 'json',
            success: function( result ) {            
                $( droplists ).each( function() {                 
                    if( this.index >= droplistJSON.index ) {                  
                        var element = $( this.jqSelector ).empty().append( $( document.createElement('option') ).html( pleaseSelectTxt ).val( 0 ) );                                      
                    }
                    if( this.index != droplistJSON.index )
                        $( element ).attr('disabled',true);
                });
                
                $( result ).each(function() {                 
                    
                    if( typeof this.timeZone != 'undefined' ) {
                        
                        $( droplistJSON.jqSelector ).append( 
                                $( document.createElement('option') )
                                    .html( this.name )
                                    .attr('timeZone',this.timeZone)
                                    .val( this.id ) )
                                .attr('disabled',false);
                    } else {
                        
                        $( droplistJSON.jqSelector ).append( 
                                $( document.createElement('option') )
                                    .html( this.name )
                                    .val( this.id ) )
                                .attr('disabled',false);                      
                    }   
                });
                if( typeof callback != 'undefined' ) callback.call(); 
            }
        });
    }   
	
	function droplistPopulateWithData( data ) {
        $.ajax({
            url: '/AjaxDroplists.do',
            data: data + '&mode=fillAll&wrapNonAirports=true',
            dataType: 'json',
            success: function( result ) {   
                $( droplists ).each(function() {                  
                    var selector = this.jqSelector;
                    var enable = false;         
                        $( selector ).empty().append( $( document.createElement('option') ).html( pleaseSelectTxt ).val( 0 ) ).attr('disabled',true);
                        
                        if (typeof(this)=='object' ) {
	                        $( result[ this.fillAllName ] ).each(function() {
	                            
	                            if( typeof this.timeZone != 'undefined' ) {
	                                
	                                $( selector ).append(
	                                        $( document.createElement('option') )
	                                            .html( this.name )
	                                            .attr('timeZone',this.timeZone)
	                                            .val( this.id )
	                                    ); 
	                                    enable = true;
	                                
	                            } else {
	                                
	                                $( selector ).append(
	                                        $( document.createElement('option') )
	                                            .html( this.name )
	                                            .val( this.id )
	                                    ); 
	                                    enable = true;                              
	                            }
	                            
	                        });  
                        }
                  
                        if( enable == true ) $( selector ).attr('disabled', false);
                        if( typeof result[ this.fillAllSelect ] != 'undefined' && result[ this.fillAllSelect ] != ''  ) {
                            $( selector ).val( result[ this.fillAllSelect ] ).find('option[value=0]').attr('disabled',true);                    
                        }                   
                });
            }
        });
    }

</script>

.time-msg {width:344px; display: none; position:relative;float:left;margin:10px 0 0;background-color: #FFFCF2;border: 1px solid #EAE6D5;color: #c00;padding: 10px;font-size: 12px;z-index:100;text-align: center;box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);-moz-box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);-webkit-box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); margin-left:10px;}
.time-msg-arrow {position:absolute;top:-16px;left:256px;width:26px;height:16px;background:url(/images/site_graphics/newsite/arrow-time-msg.png) 0 0 no-repeat;}

<script type="text/javascript" nonce="<tju:cspInlineNonce />">
    $(function() {
        $('fieldset.datetime').after(
            $( document.createElement('div') )
                .addClass('time-msg')
                .append( $( document.createElement('span') )  )
                .append( 
                    $( document.createElement('div') )
                        .addClass('time-msg-arrow')
                )
        );
        
        $('select[name=puHour], select[name=doHour], select[name=puMinute], select[name=doMinute]').change(function() {
            getHourDiff(
                $('select[name=puHour]').val(), 
                $('select[name=puMinute]').val(),
                $('select[name=doHour]').val(),
                $('select[name=doMinute]').val()
            );
        });
    });
    
    function getHourDiff(puHour, puMinute, doHour, doMinute) {      
        var puMinutes = -1;
        var doMinutes = -1;     
        try {
            puMinutes = (parseInt(puHour)*60) + parseInt(puMinute);
            doMinutes = (parseInt(doHour)*60) + parseInt(doMinute);
        } catch (e) {}
        $('.time-msg').hide();
        $('.time-msg span').html('');
        
        if(!isNaN(puMinutes)&&!isNaN(doMinutes)&&puMinutes!=-1&&doMinutes!=-1&&getPuDate().getTime()!=getDoDate().getTime()){
            var difference = doMinutes-puMinutes;
            if(difference>0&&difference<=60) {
                $('.time-msg span').html('<tju:javascriptescape>You can save a full days car rental price by reducing your rental duration by 1 hour</tju:javascriptescape>');
                $('.time-msg').show();
            } else if(difference>60&&difference<=120) {
                $('.time-msg span').html('<tju:javascriptescape>You can save a full days car rental price by reducing your rental duration by 2 hour</tju:javascriptescape>');
                $('.time-msg').show();
            } else if(difference>120&&difference<=180) {
                $('.time-msg span').html('<tju:javascriptescape>You can save a full days car rental price by reducing your rental duration by 3 hour</tju:javascriptescape>');
                $('.time-msg').show();
            }
        }       
    }

</script><fieldset id="driveragefieldset">

    /* UtmzUtils */
    (function() {

        var utmzCookieValues = null;

        function _getUtmzCookieValue() {
            var val = (document.cookie.match(/^(?:.*;)?\s__utmz=([^;]+)(?:.*)?$/)||[,null])[1];
            return val;
        }

        function _getUtmzCookieValues() {
            if (utmzCookieValues !== null) {
                return utmzCookieValues;
            }
            else {
                var utmzCookieValue = _getUtmzCookieValue();
                if (utmzCookieValue !== null) {
                    var pairs = utmzCookieValue.split('.').slice(4).join('.').split('|');
                    var ga = {};
                    for (var i = 0; i < pairs.length; i++) {
                        var temp = pairs[i].split('=');
                        ga[temp[0]] = temp[1];
                    }
                    utmzCookieValues = ga;
                    return utmzCookieValues;
                }
                else {
                    utmzCookieValues = {};
                    return utmzCookieValues;
                }
            }
        }

        function getValue(name) {
            var val = _getUtmzCookieValues()[name];
            return (typeof(val) !== 'undefined' ? val : '');
        }

        window.UtmzUtils = {
            getValue: getValue,
            _getUtmzCookieValue: _getUtmzCookieValue,
            _getUtmzCookieValues: _getUtmzCookieValues
        };

    })();
</script>

<script type="text/javascript" nonce="jlihcml4ukn80ab2ib4ackjug">
                function tagSrcIncludesPathSubstring(tag, substringTerms) {
                    var tagIncludesSubstring = false;
                    $.each(substringTerms, function(index, term) {
                        if (typeof tag.src != undefined && tag.src.indexOf(term) !== -1) {
                            tagIncludesSubstring = true;
                            return false; // breaks $.each loop
                        }
                    });

                    return tagIncludesSubstring;
                }

                function getGoogleMapCountFromTags(tags) {
                    var cnCountryOfResidence = false;
                    var googleMapUrls = cnCountryOfResidence ? ['maps.google.cn'] : ['maps.googleapis.com', 'maps.google.com'];

                    var googleMapCount = 0;
                    $.each(tags, function(index, tag) {
                        if (tagSrcIncludesPathSubstring(tag, googleMapUrls)) {
                            googleMapCount++;
                        }
                    });
                    return googleMapCount;
                }

                $(document).ready(function() {
                    var scriptTags = document.scripts;
                    var imgTags = document.images;

                    var googleMapCount = getGoogleMapCountFromTags(scriptTags);
                    var staticGoogleMapCount = getGoogleMapCountFromTags(imgTags);

                    GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'ErrorDebugInfo', 'GoogleMapScriptCount', 'PN:lp-default:'+googleMapCount, 1, true);
                    GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'ErrorDebugInfo', 'StaticGoogleMapImageCount', 'PN:lp-default:'+staticGoogleMapCount, 1, true);
                });
			</script>

          Solution

          Phase: Architecture and Design

          Use a vetted library or framework that does not allow this weakness to occur or provides constructs that make this weakness easier to avoid.

          For example, use anti-CSRF packages such as the OWASP CSRFGuard.

          Phase: Implementation

          Ensure that your application is free of cross-site scripting issues, because most CSRF defenses can be bypassed using attacker-controlled script.

          Phase: Architecture and Design

          Generate a unique nonce for each form, place the nonce into the form, and verify the nonce upon receipt of the form. Be sure that the nonce is not predictable (CWE-330).

          Note that this can be bypassed using XSS.

          Identify especially dangerous operations. When the user performs a dangerous operation, send a separate confirmation request to ensure that the user intended to perform that operation.

          Note that this can be bypassed using XSS.

          Use the ESAPI Session Management control.

          This control includes a component for CSRF.

          Do not use the GET method for any request that triggers a state change.

          Phase: Implementation

          Check the HTTP Referer header to see if the request originated from an expected page. This could break legitimate functionality, because users or proxies may have disabled sending the Referer for privacy reasons.

					function GAQPushTransition(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction) {
						serialiseEvent(new GAQEvent(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction));
					}

					function GAQPushSecureTransition(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction,domain) {
						serialiseSecureEvent(new GAQEvent(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction),domain);
					}

					function GAQPush(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction) {
						pushEvent(new GAQEvent(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction));
					}

					function GAQPushPage(gaq_event_name, action){
						pushPageEvent(new GAQPageEvent(gaq_event_name, action));
					}

					function GAQPushLinkByPost(form) {
						try {
							pushLinkByPostEvent(new GAQLinkByPostEvent(form));
						} catch(err) {
						}
					}

					$(document).ready(function() {
						try {
							if ('/LoadingSearchResults.do' !== window.location.pathname) {
								$(deserialiseEvents(true)).each(function() {
									pushEvent(this);
								});
							}
						} catch (err) {

						}
					});

					var cookie_name = 'gaw_track';

					var accountPrefixes = new Array();
					accountPrefixes.push('m');

					function serialiseEvent(gaq_event) {
						var eventList = deserialiseEvents(false);
						if (!isDuplicateGAEvent(eventList, gaq_event)) {
							eventList.push(gaq_event);
						}
						if ('' === 'true' && '' === 'true') {
							$.cookies.set(cookie_name, $.toJSON(eventList));
						}
					}

					function serialiseSecureEvent(gaq_event,domain) {
						ajaxSetCookie({
							name: cookie_name,
							value: $.toJSON(gaq_event),
							domain: domain
						});
					}

					function deserialiseEvents(deleteAfterRead) {
						var events = new Array();

						if ($.cookies.get(cookie_name) !== null) {
							var json = $.evalJSON($.toJSON($.cookies.get(cookie_name)));

							if (json instanceof Array) {
								$(json).each(function() {
									events.push(new GAQEvent(this.gaq_event_name, this.category, this.action, this.label, this.value, this.non_interaction));
								});
							}
							else {
								events.push(new GAQEvent(json.gaq_event_name, json.category, json.action, json.label, json.value, json.non_interaction));
							}
						}

						if (deleteAfterRead) {
							$.cookies.set(cookie_name, null);
						}

						return events;
					}

					function pushEvent(event) {
						try{
							_gaq.push([event.gaq_event_name, event.category, event.action, event.label, event.value, event.non_interaction]);
							for (var i = 0; i < accountPrefixes.length; i++) {
								var prefix = accountPrefixes[i];
								_gaq.push([prefix + '.' + event.gaq_event_name, event.category, event.action, event.label, event.value, event.non_interaction]);
							}
						} catch(error){
							window.console.error('Could not push to Google Analytics because: \n', error);
						}
					}

					function pushPageEvent(e) {
						try{
							_gaq.push([e.gaq_event_name, e.action]);
							for (var i = 0; i < accountPrefixes.length; i++) {
								var prefix = accountPrefixes[i];
								_gaq.push([prefix + '.' + e.gaq_event_name, e.action]);
							}
						}catch(err){

						}
					}

					function pushLinkByPostEvent(e) {
						_gaq.push([e.gaq_event_name, e.form]);
						for (var i = 0; i < accountPrefixes.length; i++) {
							var prefix = accountPrefixes[i];
							_gaq.push([prefix + '.' + e.gaq_event_name, e.form]);
						}
					}


					/*
					 * Transition management
					 * Make sure duplicate events are not tracker on page transition
					 */
					function isDuplicateGAEvent(existingEvents, newEvent) {
						var key = newEvent.category + '#' + newEvent.action + '#' + newEvent.label;
						var found = false;
						for (var i = 0; i < existingEvents.length; i++) {
							var existingEventsKey = existingEvents[i].category + '#' + existingEvents[i].action + '#' + existingEvents[i].label;
							if (existingEventsKey === key) {
								found = true;
								break;
							}
						}
						return found;
					}


					/**
					 * Object representation of the Google Analytics _gaq.push(...) method
					 * https://developers.google.com/analytics/devguides/collection/gajs/eventTrackerGuide
					 */
					function GAQEvent(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction) {
						this.gaq_event_name = gaq_event_name;
						this.category = category;
						this.action = action;
						this.label = label;
						this.value = value;
						this.non_interaction = non_interaction;
					}

					function GAQPageEvent(gaq_event_name, action) {
						this.gaq_event_name = gaq_event_name;
						this.action = action;
					}

					function GAQLinkByPostEvent(form) {
						this.gaq_event_name = '_linkByPost';
						this.form = form;
					}
				</script>

                                    $(document).ready(function(){
                                           var lcf = document.getElementById('langCurrencyForm');
                                           $('#alternative-languages a').bind('click',function(e){
                                               e.preventDefault();
                                               lcf['langCurrencyActionType'].value='language';
                                               lcf['preflang'].value=$(this).attr("id");
											   lcf['lang'].value=$(this).attr("id");
                                               try {
                                                  	GAQPushTransition('_trackEvent', 'LangChange', '361', $(this).attr("id"), 1, true);
                                                  } catch (e) {}
                                               lcf.submit();
                                           });
                                    });

<script type="text/javascript" nonce="jlihcml4ukn80ab2ib4ackjug">
       	function formSubmit()
		{
	    if( $('#show_return').attr('checked') == true ) {
            showReturnDropDown();
        }

		$('input[name=locationName]').val( $( droplists[2].jqSelector ).find('option:selected').html() );
        $('input[name=dropLocationName]').val( $( droplists[5].jqSelector ).find('option:selected').html() );
        
        if( $( droplists[2].jqSelector ).val() == -1 && $( droplists[5].jqSelector ).val() == -1 ) {
            
            if( $( droplists[0].jqSelector ).val() == $( droplists[3].jqSelector ).val() && $( droplists[1].jqSelector ).val() == $( droplists[4].jqSelector ).val() ) {
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=searchType]').val('allareasgeosearch');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=doFiltering]').val('true');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterTo]').val('20');
            } else {                          
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=searchType]').val('manytomanysearch');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=doFiltering]').val('true');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterTo]').val('20');
            }
    
        } else if(  $( droplists[2].jqSelector ).val() == -1 && $( droplists[5].jqSelector ).val() != -1 ) {
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=searchType]').val('manytoonesearch');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=doFiltering]').val('true');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterTo]').val('20');
        } else if(  $( droplists[2].jqSelector ).val() != -1 && $( droplists[5].jqSelector ).val() == -1 ) {
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=searchType]').val('onetomanysearch');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=doFiltering]').val('true');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterTo]').val('20');
        } else {
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=searchType]').val('');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=doFiltering]').val('false');
        	$('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterTo]').val('1000');
        }
       

		if(validateSearchResultsForm( document.SearchResultsForm ) ) {			
			saveInput();
			$('form[name=SearchResultsForm]').append(
                    $( document.createElement('input') )
                        .attr('type','hidden')
                        .attr('name','fromLocChoose')
                        .val(true)
                );
			$('form[name=SearchResultsForm]').submit();      
		}else {
			return false;
		}
	}
	
	 function droplistPopulate( data, droplistJSON, callback ) {
        $.ajax({
            url: '/AjaxDroplists.do',
            data: data + '&wrapNonAirports=true',
            dataType: 'json',
            success: function( result ) {            
                $( droplists ).each( function() {                 
                    if( this.index >= droplistJSON.index ) {                  
                        var element = $( this.jqSelector ).empty().append( $( document.createElement('option') ).html( pleaseSelectTxt ).val( 0 ) );                                      
                    }
                    if( this.index != droplistJSON.index )
                        $( element ).attr('disabled',true);
                });
                
                $( result ).each(function() {                 
                    
                    if( typeof this.timeZone != 'undefined' ) {
                        
                        $( droplistJSON.jqSelector ).append( 
                                $( document.createElement('option') )
                                    .html( this.name )
                                    .attr('timeZone',this.timeZone)
                                    .val( this.id ) )
                                .attr('disabled',false);
                    } else {
                        
                        $( droplistJSON.jqSelector ).append( 
                                $( document.createElement('option') )
                                    .html( this.name )
                                    .val( this.id ) )
                                .attr('disabled',false);                      
                    }   
                });
                if( typeof callback != 'undefined' ) callback.call(); 
            }
        });
    }   
	
	function droplistPopulateWithData( data ) {
        $.ajax({
            url: '/AjaxDroplists.do',
            data: data + '&mode=fillAll&wrapNonAirports=true',
            dataType: 'json',
            success: function( result ) {   
                $( droplists ).each(function() {                  
                    var selector = this.jqSelector;
                    var enable = false;         
                        $( selector ).empty().append( $( document.createElement('option') ).html( pleaseSelectTxt ).val( 0 ) ).attr('disabled',true);
                        
                        if (typeof(this)=='object' ) {
	                        $( result[ this.fillAllName ] ).each(function() {
	                            
	                            if( typeof this.timeZone != 'undefined' ) {
	                                
	                                $( selector ).append(
	                                        $( document.createElement('option') )
	                                            .html( this.name )
	                                            .attr('timeZone',this.timeZone)
	                                            .val( this.id )
	                                    ); 
	                                    enable = true;
	                                
	                            } else {
	                                
	                                $( selector ).append(
	                                        $( document.createElement('option') )
	                                            .html( this.name )
	                                            .val( this.id )
	                                    ); 
	                                    enable = true;                              
	                            }
	                            
	                        });  
                        }
                  
                        if( enable == true ) $( selector ).attr('disabled', false);
                        if( typeof result[ this.fillAllSelect ] != 'undefined' && result[ this.fillAllSelect ] != ''  ) {
                            $( selector ).val( result[ this.fillAllSelect ] ).find('option[value=0]').attr('disabled',true);                    
                        }                   
                });
            }
        });
    }

</script>

<script type="text/javascript" nonce="<tju:cspInlineNonce />">
    $(function() {
        $('fieldset.datetime').after(
            $( document.createElement('div') )
                .addClass('time-msg')
                .append( $( document.createElement('span') )  )
                .append( 
                    $( document.createElement('div') )
                        .addClass('time-msg-arrow')
                )
        );
        
        $('select[name=puHour], select[name=doHour], select[name=puMinute], select[name=doMinute]').change(function() {
            getHourDiff(
                $('select[name=puHour]').val(), 
                $('select[name=puMinute]').val(),
                $('select[name=doHour]').val(),
                $('select[name=doMinute]').val()
            );
        });
    });
    
    function getHourDiff(puHour, puMinute, doHour, doMinute) {      
        var puMinutes = -1;
        var doMinutes = -1;     
        try {
            puMinutes = (parseInt(puHour)*60) + parseInt(puMinute);
            doMinutes = (parseInt(doHour)*60) + parseInt(doMinute);
        } catch (e) {}
        $('.time-msg').hide();
        $('.time-msg span').html('');
        
        if(!isNaN(puMinutes)&&!isNaN(doMinutes)&&puMinutes!=-1&&doMinutes!=-1&&getPuDate().getTime()!=getDoDate().getTime()){
            var difference = doMinutes-puMinutes;
            if(difference>0&&difference<=60) {
                $('.time-msg span').html('<tju:javascriptescape>You can save a full days car rental price by reducing your rental duration by 1 hour</tju:javascriptescape>');
                $('.time-msg').show();
            } else if(difference>60&&difference<=120) {
                $('.time-msg span').html('<tju:javascriptescape>You can save a full days car rental price by reducing your rental duration by 2 hour</tju:javascriptescape>');
                $('.time-msg').show();
            } else if(difference>120&&difference<=180) {
                $('.time-msg span').html('<tju:javascriptescape>You can save a full days car rental price by reducing your rental duration by 3 hour</tju:javascriptescape>');
                $('.time-msg').show();
            }
        }       
    }

<script type="text/javascript" nonce="jlihcml4ukn80ab2ib4ackjug">
    /* UtmzUtils */
    (function() {

        var utmzCookieValues = null;

        function _getUtmzCookieValue() {
            var val = (document.cookie.match(/^(?:.*;)?\s__utmz=([^;]+)(?:.*)?$/)||[,null])[1];
            return val;
        }

        function _getUtmzCookieValues() {
            if (utmzCookieValues !== null) {
                return utmzCookieValues;
            }
            else {
                var utmzCookieValue = _getUtmzCookieValue();
                if (utmzCookieValue !== null) {
                    var pairs = utmzCookieValue.split('.').slice(4).join('.').split('|');
                    var ga = {};
                    for (var i = 0; i < pairs.length; i++) {
                        var temp = pairs[i].split('=');
                        ga[temp[0]] = temp[1];
                    }
                    utmzCookieValues = ga;
                    return utmzCookieValues;
                }

<script type="text/javascript" nonce="jlihcml4ukn80ab2ib4ackjug">
                function tagSrcIncludesPathSubstring(tag, substringTerms) {
                    var tagIncludesSubstring = false;
                    $.each(substringTerms, function(index, term) {
                        if (typeof tag.src != undefined && tag.src.indexOf(term) !== -1) {
                            tagIncludesSubstring = true;
                            return false; // breaks $.each loop
                        }
                    });

                    return tagIncludesSubstring;
                }

                function getGoogleMapCountFromTags(tags) {
                    var cnCountryOfResidence = false;
                    var googleMapUrls = cnCountryOfResidence ? ['maps.google.cn'] : ['maps.googleapis.com', 'maps.google.com'];

                    var googleMapCount = 0;
                    $.each(tags, function(index, tag) {
                        if (tagSrcIncludesPathSubstring(tag, googleMapUrls)) {
                            googleMapCount++;
                        }
                    });
                    return googleMapCount;
                }

                $(document).ready(function() {
                    var scriptTags = document.scripts;
                    var imgTags = document.images;

                    var googleMapCount = getGoogleMapCountFromTags(scriptTags);
                    var staticGoogleMapCount = getGoogleMapCountFromTags(imgTags);

                    GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'ErrorDebugInfo', 'GoogleMapScriptCount', 'PN:lp-default:'+googleMapCount, 1, true);
                    GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'ErrorDebugInfo', 'StaticGoogleMapImageCount', 'PN:lp-default:'+staticGoogleMapCount, 1, true);
                });

    var group;
    if( $.cookies.get('group') != null ) {
        group = $.cookies.get('group');
    } else {
    	random = Math.floor(Math.random() * 3);
    	
    	if (random == 0)
    		group = 'A'
    	else if (random == 1)
    		group = 'B'
    	else
    		group = 'C';

					$(document).ready(function() {
						try {
							if ('/LoadingSearchResults.do' !== window.location.pathname) {
								$(deserialiseEvents(true)).each(function() {
									pushEvent(this);
								});
