       	function formSubmit()
		{
	    if( $('#show_return').attr('checked') == true ) {
            showReturnDropDown();
        }

		$('input[name=locationName]').val( $( droplists[2].jqSelector ).find('option:selected').html() );
        $('input[name=dropLocationName]').val( $( droplists[5].jqSelector ).find('option:selected').html() );
        
        if( $( droplists[2].jqSelector ).val() == -1 && $( droplists[5].jqSelector ).val() == -1 ) {
            
            if( $( droplists[0].jqSelector ).val() == $( droplists[3].jqSelector ).val() && $( droplists[1].jqSelector ).val() == $( droplists[4].jqSelector ).val() ) {
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=searchType]').val('allareasgeosearch');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=doFiltering]').val('true');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterTo]').val('20');
            } else {                          
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=searchType]').val('manytomanysearch');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=doFiltering]').val('true');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterTo]').val('20');
            }
    
        } else if(  $( droplists[2].jqSelector ).val() == -1 && $( droplists[5].jqSelector ).val() != -1 ) {
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=searchType]').val('manytoonesearch');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=doFiltering]').val('true');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterTo]').val('20');
        } else if(  $( droplists[2].jqSelector ).val() != -1 && $( droplists[5].jqSelector ).val() == -1 ) {
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=searchType]').val('onetomanysearch');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=doFiltering]').val('true');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterTo]').val('20');
        } else {
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=searchType]').val('');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=doFiltering]').val('false');
        	$('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterTo]').val('1000');
        }
       

		if(validateSearchResultsForm( document.SearchResultsForm ) ) {			
			saveInput();
			$('form[name=SearchResultsForm]').append(
                    $( document.createElement('input') )
                        .attr('type','hidden')
                        .attr('name','fromLocChoose')
                        .val(true)
                );
			$('form[name=SearchResultsForm]').submit();      
		}else {
			return false;
		}
	}
	
	 function droplistPopulate( data, droplistJSON, callback ) {
        $.ajax({
            url: '/AjaxDroplists.do',
            data: data + '&wrapNonAirports=true',
            dataType: 'json',
            success: function( result ) {            
                $( droplists ).each( function() {                 
                    if( this.index >= droplistJSON.index ) {                  
                        var element = $( this.jqSelector ).empty().append( $( document.createElement('option') ).html( pleaseSelectTxt ).val( 0 ) );                                      
                    }
                    if( this.index != droplistJSON.index )
                        $( element ).attr('disabled',true);
                });
                
                $( result ).each(function() {                 
                    
                    if( typeof this.timeZone != 'undefined' ) {
                        
                        $( droplistJSON.jqSelector ).append( 
                                $( document.createElement('option') )
                                    .html( this.name )
                                    .attr('timeZone',this.timeZone)
                                    .val( this.id ) )
                                .attr('disabled',false);
                    } else {
                        
                        $( droplistJSON.jqSelector ).append( 
                                $( document.createElement('option') )
                                    .html( this.name )
                                    .val( this.id ) )
                                .attr('disabled',false);                      
                    }   
                });
                if( typeof callback != 'undefined' ) callback.call(); 
            }
        });
    }   
	
	function droplistPopulateWithData( data ) {
        $.ajax({
            url: '/AjaxDroplists.do',
            data: data + '&mode=fillAll&wrapNonAirports=true',
            dataType: 'json',
            success: function( result ) {   
                $( droplists ).each(function() {                  
                    var selector = this.jqSelector;
                    var enable = false;         
                        $( selector ).empty().append( $( document.createElement('option') ).html( pleaseSelectTxt ).val( 0 ) ).attr('disabled',true);
                        
                        if (typeof(this)=='object' ) {
	                        $( result[ this.fillAllName ] ).each(function() {
	                            
	                            if( typeof this.timeZone != 'undefined' ) {
	                                
	                                $( selector ).append(
	                                        $( document.createElement('option') )
	                                            .html( this.name )
	                                            .attr('timeZone',this.timeZone)
	                                            .val( this.id )
	                                    ); 
	                                    enable = true;
	                                
	                            } else {
	                                
	                                $( selector ).append(
	                                        $( document.createElement('option') )
	                                            .html( this.name )
	                                            .val( this.id )
	                                    ); 
	                                    enable = true;                              
	                            }
	                            
	                        });  
                        }
                  
                        if( enable == true ) $( selector ).attr('disabled', false);
                        if( typeof result[ this.fillAllSelect ] != 'undefined' && result[ this.fillAllSelect ] != ''  ) {
                            $( selector ).val( result[ this.fillAllSelect ] ).find('option[value=0]').attr('disabled',true);                    
                        }                   
                });
            }
        });
    }

<script type="text/javascript" nonce="<tju:cspInlineNonce />">
    $(function() {
        $('fieldset.datetime').after(
            $( document.createElement('div') )
                .addClass('time-msg')
                .append( $( document.createElement('span') )  )
                .append( 
                    $( document.createElement('div') )
                        .addClass('time-msg-arrow')
                )
        );
        
        $('select[name=puHour], select[name=doHour], select[name=puMinute], select[name=doMinute]').change(function() {
            getHourDiff(
                $('select[name=puHour]').val(), 
                $('select[name=puMinute]').val(),
                $('select[name=doHour]').val(),
                $('select[name=doMinute]').val()
            );
        });
    });
    
    function getHourDiff(puHour, puMinute, doHour, doMinute) {      
        var puMinutes = -1;
        var doMinutes = -1;     
        try {
            puMinutes = (parseInt(puHour)*60) + parseInt(puMinute);
            doMinutes = (parseInt(doHour)*60) + parseInt(doMinute);
        } catch (e) {}
        $('.time-msg').hide();
        $('.time-msg span').html('');
        
        if(!isNaN(puMinutes)&&!isNaN(doMinutes)&&puMinutes!=-1&&doMinutes!=-1&&getPuDate().getTime()!=getDoDate().getTime()){
            var difference = doMinutes-puMinutes;
            if(difference>0&&difference<=60) {
                $('.time-msg span').html('<tju:javascriptescape>You can save a full days car rental price by reducing your rental duration by 1 hour</tju:javascriptescape>');
                $('.time-msg').show();
            } else if(difference>60&&difference<=120) {
                $('.time-msg span').html('<tju:javascriptescape>You can save a full days car rental price by reducing your rental duration by 2 hour</tju:javascriptescape>');
                $('.time-msg').show();
            } else if(difference>120&&difference<=180) {
                $('.time-msg span').html('<tju:javascriptescape>You can save a full days car rental price by reducing your rental duration by 3 hour</tju:javascriptescape>');
                $('.time-msg').show();
            }
        }       
    }

    (function() {

        var utmzCookieValues = null;

        function _getUtmzCookieValue() {
            var val = (document.cookie.match(/^(?:.*;)?\s__utmz=([^;]+)(?:.*)?$/)||[,null])[1];
            return val;
        }

        function _getUtmzCookieValues() {
            if (utmzCookieValues !== null) {
                return utmzCookieValues;
            }
            else {
                var utmzCookieValue = _getUtmzCookieValue();
                if (utmzCookieValue !== null) {
                    var pairs = utmzCookieValue.split('.').slice(4).join('.').split('|');
                    var ga = {};
                    for (var i = 0; i < pairs.length; i++) {
                        var temp = pairs[i].split('=');
                        ga[temp[0]] = temp[1];
                    }
                    utmzCookieValues = ga;
                    return utmzCookieValues;
                }
                else {
                    utmzCookieValues = {};
                    return utmzCookieValues;
                }
            }
        }

        function getValue(name) {
            var val = _getUtmzCookieValues()[name];
            return (typeof(val) !== 'undefined' ? val : '');
        }

        window.UtmzUtils = {
            getValue: getValue,
            _getUtmzCookieValue: _getUtmzCookieValue,
            _getUtmzCookieValues: _getUtmzCookieValues
        };

    })();

                function tagSrcIncludesPathSubstring(tag, substringTerms) {
                    var tagIncludesSubstring = false;
                    $.each(substringTerms, function(index, term) {
                        if (typeof tag.src != undefined && tag.src.indexOf(term) !== -1) {
                            tagIncludesSubstring = true;
                            return false; // breaks $.each loop
                        }
                    });

                    return tagIncludesSubstring;
                }

                function getGoogleMapCountFromTags(tags) {
                    var cnCountryOfResidence = false;
                    var googleMapUrls = cnCountryOfResidence ? ['maps.google.cn'] : ['maps.googleapis.com', 'maps.google.com'];

                    var googleMapCount = 0;
                    $.each(tags, function(index, tag) {
                        if (tagSrcIncludesPathSubstring(tag, googleMapUrls)) {
                            googleMapCount++;
                        }
                    });
                    return googleMapCount;
                }

                $(document).ready(function() {
                    var scriptTags = document.scripts;

					function GAQPushTransition(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction) {
						serialiseEvent(new GAQEvent(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction));
					}

					function GAQPushSecureTransition(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction,domain) {
						serialiseSecureEvent(new GAQEvent(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction),domain);
					}

					function GAQPush(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction) {
						pushEvent(new GAQEvent(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction));
					}

					function GAQPushPage(gaq_event_name, action){
						pushPageEvent(new GAQPageEvent(gaq_event_name, action));
					}

					function GAQPushLinkByPost(form) {
						try {
							pushLinkByPostEvent(new GAQLinkByPostEvent(form));
						} catch(err) {
						}
					}

					$(document).ready(function() {
						try {
							if ('/LoadingSearchResults.do' !== window.location.pathname) {
								$(deserialiseEvents(true)).each(function() {
									pushEvent(this);
								});
							}
						} catch (err) {

						}
					});

					var cookie_name = 'gaw_track';

					var accountPrefixes = new Array();
					accountPrefixes.push('m');

					function serialiseEvent(gaq_event) {
						var eventList = deserialiseEvents(false);
						if (!isDuplicateGAEvent(eventList, gaq_event)) {
							eventList.push(gaq_event);
						}
						if ('' === 'true' && '' === 'true') {
							$.cookies.set(cookie_name, $.toJSON(eventList));
						}
					}

					function serialiseSecureEvent(gaq_event,domain) {
						ajaxSetCookie({
							name: cookie_name,
							value: $.toJSON(gaq_event),
							domain: domain
						});
					}

					function deserialiseEvents(deleteAfterRead) {
						var events = new Array();

						if ($.cookies.get(cookie_name) !== null) {
							var json = $.evalJSON($.toJSON($.cookies.get(cookie_name)));

							if (json instanceof Array) {
								$(json).each(function() {
									events.push(new GAQEvent(this.gaq_event_name, this.category, this.action, this.label, this.value, this.non_interaction));
								});
							}
							else {
								events.push(new GAQEvent(json.gaq_event_name, json.category, json.action, json.label, json.value, json.non_interaction));
							}
						}

						if (deleteAfterRead) {
							$.cookies.set(cookie_name, null);
						}

						return events;
					}

					function pushEvent(event) {
						try{
							_gaq.push([event.gaq_event_name, event.category, event.action, event.label, event.value, event.non_interaction]);
							for (var i = 0; i < accountPrefixes.length; i++) {
								var prefix = accountPrefixes[i];
								_gaq.push([prefix + '.' + event.gaq_event_name, event.category, event.action, event.label, event.value, event.non_interaction]);
							}
						} catch(error){
							window.console.error('Could not push to Google Analytics because: \n', error);
						}
					}

					function pushPageEvent(e) {
						try{
							_gaq.push([e.gaq_event_name, e.action]);
							for (var i = 0; i < accountPrefixes.length; i++) {
								var prefix = accountPrefixes[i];
								_gaq.push([prefix + '.' + e.gaq_event_name, e.action]);
							}
						}catch(err){

						}
					}

					function pushLinkByPostEvent(e) {
						_gaq.push([e.gaq_event_name, e.form]);
						for (var i = 0; i < accountPrefixes.length; i++) {
							var prefix = accountPrefixes[i];
							_gaq.push([prefix + '.' + e.gaq_event_name, e.form]);
						}
					}


					/*
					 * Transition management
					 * Make sure duplicate events are not tracker on page transition
					 */
					function isDuplicateGAEvent(existingEvents, newEvent) {
						var key = newEvent.category + '#' + newEvent.action + '#' + newEvent.label;
						var found = false;
						for (var i = 0; i < existingEvents.length; i++) {
							var existingEventsKey = existingEvents[i].category + '#' + existingEvents[i].action + '#' + existingEvents[i].label;
							if (existingEventsKey === key) {
								found = true;
								break;
							}
						}
						return found;
					}


					/**
					 * Object representation of the Google Analytics _gaq.push(...) method
					 * https://developers.google.com/analytics/devguides/collection/gajs/eventTrackerGuide
					 */
					function GAQEvent(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction) {
						this.gaq_event_name = gaq_event_name;
						this.category = category;
						this.action = action;
						this.label = label;
						this.value = value;
						this.non_interaction = non_interaction;
					}

					function GAQPageEvent(gaq_event_name, action) {
						this.gaq_event_name = gaq_event_name;
						this.action = action;
					}

					function GAQLinkByPostEvent(form) {
						this.gaq_event_name = '_linkByPost';
						this.form = form;
					}
				</script>

                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');

	 function droplistPopulate( data, droplistJSON, callback ) {
        $.ajax({
            url: '/AjaxDroplists.do',
            data: data + '&wrapNonAirports=true',
            dataType: 'json',
            success: function( result ) {            
                $( droplists ).each( function() {                 
                    if( this.index >= droplistJSON.index ) {                  
                        var element = $( this.jqSelector ).empty().append( $( document.createElement('option') ).html( pleaseSelectTxt ).val( 0 ) );                                      
                    }
                    if( this.index != droplistJSON.index )
                        $( element ).attr('disabled',true);
                });
                
                $( result ).each(function() {                 
                    
                    if( typeof this.timeZone != 'undefined' ) {
                        
                        $( droplistJSON.jqSelector ).append( 
                                $( document.createElement('option') )
                                    .html( this.name )
                                    .attr('timeZone',this.timeZone)
                                    .val( this.id ) )
                                .attr('disabled',false);
                    } else {
                        
                        $( droplistJSON.jqSelector ).append( 
                                $( document.createElement('option') )
                                    .html( this.name )
                                    .val( this.id ) )
                                .attr('disabled',false);                      
                    }   
                });
                if( typeof callback != 'undefined' ) callback.call(); 
            }
        });
    }   
	
	function droplistPopulateWithData( data ) {
        $.ajax({
            url: '/AjaxDroplists.do',
            data: data + '&mode=fillAll&wrapNonAirports=true',
            dataType: 'json',
            success: function( result ) {   
                $( droplists ).each(function() {                  
                    var selector = this.jqSelector;
                    var enable = false;         
                        $( selector ).empty().append( $( document.createElement('option') ).html( pleaseSelectTxt ).val( 0 ) ).attr('disabled',true);
                        
                        if (typeof(this)=='object' ) {
	                        $( result[ this.fillAllName ] ).each(function() {
	                            
	                            if( typeof this.timeZone != 'undefined' ) {
	                                
	                                $( selector ).append(
	                                        $( document.createElement('option') )
	                                            .html( this.name )
	                                            .attr('timeZone',this.timeZone)
	                                            .val( this.id )
	                                    ); 
	                                    enable = true;
	                                
	                            } else {
	                                
	                                $( selector ).append(
	                                        $( document.createElement('option') )
	                                            .html( this.name )
	                                            .val( this.id )
	                                    ); 
	                                    enable = true;                              
	                            }
	                            
	                        });  
                        }
                  
                        if( enable == true ) $( selector ).attr('disabled', false);
                        if( typeof result[ this.fillAllSelect ] != 'undefined' && result[ this.fillAllSelect ] != ''  ) {
                            $( selector ).val( result[ this.fillAllSelect ] ).find('option[value=0]').attr('disabled',true);                    
                        }                   
                });
            }
        });
    }

<script type="text/javascript" nonce="<tju:cspInlineNonce />">
    $(function() {
        $('fieldset.datetime').after(
            $( document.createElement('div') )
                .addClass('time-msg')
                .append( $( document.createElement('span') )  )
                .append( 
                    $( document.createElement('div') )
                        .addClass('time-msg-arrow')
                )
        );
        
        $('select[name=puHour], select[name=doHour], select[name=puMinute], select[name=doMinute]').change(function() {
            getHourDiff(
                $('select[name=puHour]').val(), 
                $('select[name=puMinute]').val(),
                $('select[name=doHour]').val(),
                $('select[name=doMinute]').val()
            );
        });
    });
    
    function getHourDiff(puHour, puMinute, doHour, doMinute) {      
        var puMinutes = -1;
        var doMinutes = -1;     
        try {
            puMinutes = (parseInt(puHour)*60) + parseInt(puMinute);
            doMinutes = (parseInt(doHour)*60) + parseInt(doMinute);
        } catch (e) {}
        $('.time-msg').hide();
        $('.time-msg span').html('');
        
        if(!isNaN(puMinutes)&&!isNaN(doMinutes)&&puMinutes!=-1&&doMinutes!=-1&&getPuDate().getTime()!=getDoDate().getTime()){
            var difference = doMinutes-puMinutes;
            if(difference>0&&difference<=60) {
                $('.time-msg span').html('<tju:javascriptescape>You can save a full days car rental price by reducing your rental duration by 1 hour</tju:javascriptescape>');
                $('.time-msg').show();
            } else if(difference>60&&difference<=120) {
                $('.time-msg span').html('<tju:javascriptescape>You can save a full days car rental price by reducing your rental duration by 2 hour</tju:javascriptescape>');
                $('.time-msg').show();
            } else if(difference>120&&difference<=180) {
                $('.time-msg span').html('<tju:javascriptescape>You can save a full days car rental price by reducing your rental duration by 3 hour</tju:javascriptescape>');
                $('.time-msg').show();
            }
        }       
    }

    (function() {

        var utmzCookieValues = null;

        function _getUtmzCookieValue() {
            var val = (document.cookie.match(/^(?:.*;)?\s__utmz=([^;]+)(?:.*)?$/)||[,null])[1];
            return val;
        }

        function _getUtmzCookieValues() {
            if (utmzCookieValues !== null) {
                return utmzCookieValues;
            }
            else {
                var utmzCookieValue = _getUtmzCookieValue();
                if (utmzCookieValue !== null) {
                    var pairs = utmzCookieValue.split('.').slice(4).join('.').split('|');
                    var ga = {};
                    for (var i = 0; i < pairs.length; i++) {
                        var temp = pairs[i].split('=');
                        ga[temp[0]] = temp[1];
                    }
                    utmzCookieValues = ga;
                    return utmzCookieValues;
                }
                else {
                    utmzCookieValues = {};
                    return utmzCookieValues;
                }
            }
        }

        function getValue(name) {
            var val = _getUtmzCookieValues()[name];
            return (typeof(val) !== 'undefined' ? val : '');
        }

        window.UtmzUtils = {
            getValue: getValue,
            _getUtmzCookieValue: _getUtmzCookieValue,
            _getUtmzCookieValues: _getUtmzCookieValues
        };

    })();

                function tagSrcIncludesPathSubstring(tag, substringTerms) {
                    var tagIncludesSubstring = false;
                    $.each(substringTerms, function(index, term) {
                        if (typeof tag.src != undefined && tag.src.indexOf(term) !== -1) {
                            tagIncludesSubstring = true;
                            return false; // breaks $.each loop
                        }
                    });

                    return tagIncludesSubstring;
                }

                function getGoogleMapCountFromTags(tags) {
                    var cnCountryOfResidence = false;
                    var googleMapUrls = cnCountryOfResidence ? ['maps.google.cn'] : ['maps.googleapis.com', 'maps.google.com'];

                    var googleMapCount = 0;
                    $.each(tags, function(index, tag) {
                        if (tagSrcIncludesPathSubstring(tag, googleMapUrls)) {
                            googleMapCount++;
                        }
                    });
                    return googleMapCount;
                }

      1. Cookie Poisoning (1)
        1. GET https://widget.rentalcars.com/AjaxSetCookie.do?name=rv&value=1
          Alert tags
          • OWASP_2021_A03
          • OWASP_2017_A01
          Alert description

          This check looks at user-supplied input in query string parameters and POST data to identify where cookie parameters might be controlled. This is called a cookie poisoning attack, and becomes exploitable when an attacker can manipulate the cookie in various ways. In some cases this will not be exploitable, however, allowing URL parameters to set cookie values is generally considered a bug.
          Other info

          An attacker may be able to poison cookie values through URL parameters. Try injecting a semicolon to see if you can add cookie values (e.g. name=controlledValue;name=anotherValue;).

					function GAQPushTransition(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction) {
						serialiseEvent(new GAQEvent(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction));
					}

					function GAQPushSecureTransition(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction,domain) {
						serialiseSecureEvent(new GAQEvent(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction),domain);
					}

					function GAQPush(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction) {
						pushEvent(new GAQEvent(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction));
					}

					function GAQPushPage(gaq_event_name, action){
						pushPageEvent(new GAQPageEvent(gaq_event_name, action));
					}

					function GAQPushLinkByPost(form) {
						try {
							pushLinkByPostEvent(new GAQLinkByPostEvent(form));
						} catch(err) {
						}
					}

					$(document).ready(function() {
						try {
							if ('/LoadingSearchResults.do' !== window.location.pathname) {
								$(deserialiseEvents(true)).each(function() {
									pushEvent(this);
								});
							}
						} catch (err) {

						}
					});

					var cookie_name = 'gaw_track';

					var accountPrefixes = new Array();
					accountPrefixes.push('m');

					function serialiseEvent(gaq_event) {
						var eventList = deserialiseEvents(false);
						if (!isDuplicateGAEvent(eventList, gaq_event)) {
							eventList.push(gaq_event);
						}
						if ('' === 'true' && '' === 'true') {
							$.cookies.set(cookie_name, $.toJSON(eventList));
						}
					}

					function serialiseSecureEvent(gaq_event,domain) {
						ajaxSetCookie({
							name: cookie_name,
							value: $.toJSON(gaq_event),
							domain: domain
						});
					}

					function deserialiseEvents(deleteAfterRead) {
						var events = new Array();

						if ($.cookies.get(cookie_name) !== null) {
							var json = $.evalJSON($.toJSON($.cookies.get(cookie_name)));

							if (json instanceof Array) {
								$(json).each(function() {
									events.push(new GAQEvent(this.gaq_event_name, this.category, this.action, this.label, this.value, this.non_interaction));
								});
							}
							else {
								events.push(new GAQEvent(json.gaq_event_name, json.category, json.action, json.label, json.value, json.non_interaction));
							}
						}

						if (deleteAfterRead) {
							$.cookies.set(cookie_name, null);
						}

						return events;
					}

					function pushEvent(event) {
						try{
							_gaq.push([event.gaq_event_name, event.category, event.action, event.label, event.value, event.non_interaction]);
							for (var i = 0; i < accountPrefixes.length; i++) {
								var prefix = accountPrefixes[i];
								_gaq.push([prefix + '.' + event.gaq_event_name, event.category, event.action, event.label, event.value, event.non_interaction]);
							}
						} catch(error){
							window.console.error('Could not push to Google Analytics because: \n', error);
						}
					}

					function pushPageEvent(e) {
						try{
							_gaq.push([e.gaq_event_name, e.action]);
							for (var i = 0; i < accountPrefixes.length; i++) {
								var prefix = accountPrefixes[i];
								_gaq.push([prefix + '.' + e.gaq_event_name, e.action]);
							}
						}catch(err){

						}
					}

					function pushLinkByPostEvent(e) {
						_gaq.push([e.gaq_event_name, e.form]);
						for (var i = 0; i < accountPrefixes.length; i++) {
							var prefix = accountPrefixes[i];
							_gaq.push([prefix + '.' + e.gaq_event_name, e.form]);
						}
					}


					/*
					 * Transition management
					 * Make sure duplicate events are not tracker on page transition
					 */
					function isDuplicateGAEvent(existingEvents, newEvent) {
						var key = newEvent.category + '#' + newEvent.action + '#' + newEvent.label;
						var found = false;
						for (var i = 0; i < existingEvents.length; i++) {
							var existingEventsKey = existingEvents[i].category + '#' + existingEvents[i].action + '#' + existingEvents[i].label;
							if (existingEventsKey === key) {
								found = true;
								break;
							}
						}
						return found;
					}


					/**
					 * Object representation of the Google Analytics _gaq.push(...) method
					 * https://developers.google.com/analytics/devguides/collection/gajs/eventTrackerGuide
					 */
					function GAQEvent(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction) {
						this.gaq_event_name = gaq_event_name;
						this.category = category;
						this.action = action;
						this.label = label;
						this.value = value;
						this.non_interaction = non_interaction;
					}

					function GAQPageEvent(gaq_event_name, action) {
						this.gaq_event_name = gaq_event_name;
						this.action = action;
					}

					function GAQLinkByPostEvent(form) {
						this.gaq_event_name = '_linkByPost';
						this.form = form;
					}
				</script>

                                    $(document).ready(function(){
                                           var lcf = document.getElementById('langCurrencyForm');
                                           $('#alternative-languages a').bind('click',function(e){
                                               e.preventDefault();
                                               lcf['langCurrencyActionType'].value='language';
                                               lcf['preflang'].value=$(this).attr("id");
											   lcf['lang'].value=$(this).attr("id");
                                               try {
                                                  	GAQPushTransition('_trackEvent', 'LangChange', '361', $(this).attr("id"), 1, true);
                                                  } catch (e) {}
                                               lcf.submit();
                                           });
                                    });

	function createAccountTrack() {
		GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'CRM Event', 'New CRM Account', "Desktop: CRM Header, Pay Now", 1, true);
		return createAccount();

		GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'CRM Event', 'New CRM Login', "Desktop: CRM Header, Pay Now", 1, true);

<script type="text/javascript" nonce="jlihcml4ukn80ab2ib4ackjug">
       	function formSubmit()
		{
	    if( $('#show_return').attr('checked') == true ) {
            showReturnDropDown();
        }

		$('input[name=locationName]').val( $( droplists[2].jqSelector ).find('option:selected').html() );
        $('input[name=dropLocationName]').val( $( droplists[5].jqSelector ).find('option:selected').html() );
        
        if( $( droplists[2].jqSelector ).val() == -1 && $( droplists[5].jqSelector ).val() == -1 ) {
            
            if( $( droplists[0].jqSelector ).val() == $( droplists[3].jqSelector ).val() && $( droplists[1].jqSelector ).val() == $( droplists[4].jqSelector ).val() ) {
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=searchType]').val('allareasgeosearch');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=doFiltering]').val('true');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterTo]').val('20');
            } else {                          
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=searchType]').val('manytomanysearch');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=doFiltering]').val('true');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterTo]').val('20');
            }
    
        } else if(  $( droplists[2].jqSelector ).val() == -1 && $( droplists[5].jqSelector ).val() != -1 ) {
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=searchType]').val('manytoonesearch');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=doFiltering]').val('true');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterTo]').val('20');
        } else if(  $( droplists[2].jqSelector ).val() != -1 && $( droplists[5].jqSelector ).val() == -1 ) {
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=searchType]').val('onetomanysearch');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=doFiltering]').val('true');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterTo]').val('20');
        } else {
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=searchType]').val('');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=doFiltering]').val('false');
        	$('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterTo]').val('1000');
        }
       

		if(validateSearchResultsForm( document.SearchResultsForm ) ) {			
			saveInput();
			$('form[name=SearchResultsForm]').append(
                    $( document.createElement('input') )
                        .attr('type','hidden')
                        .attr('name','fromLocChoose')
                        .val(true)
                );
			$('form[name=SearchResultsForm]').submit();      
		}else {
			return false;
		}
	}
	
	 function droplistPopulate( data, droplistJSON, callback ) {
        $.ajax({
            url: '/AjaxDroplists.do',
            data: data + '&wrapNonAirports=true',
            dataType: 'json',
            success: function( result ) {            
                $( droplists ).each( function() {                 
                    if( this.index >= droplistJSON.index ) {                  
                        var element = $( this.jqSelector ).empty().append( $( document.createElement('option') ).html( pleaseSelectTxt ).val( 0 ) );                                      
                    }
                    if( this.index != droplistJSON.index )
                        $( element ).attr('disabled',true);
                });
                
                $( result ).each(function() {                 
                    
                    if( typeof this.timeZone != 'undefined' ) {
                        
                        $( droplistJSON.jqSelector ).append( 
                                $( document.createElement('option') )
                                    .html( this.name )
                                    .attr('timeZone',this.timeZone)
                                    .val( this.id ) )
                                .attr('disabled',false);
                    } else {
                        
                        $( droplistJSON.jqSelector ).append( 
                                $( document.createElement('option') )
                                    .html( this.name )
                                    .val( this.id ) )
                                .attr('disabled',false);                      
                    }   
                });
                if( typeof callback != 'undefined' ) callback.call(); 
            }
        });
    }   
	
	function droplistPopulateWithData( data ) {
        $.ajax({
            url: '/AjaxDroplists.do',
            data: data + '&mode=fillAll&wrapNonAirports=true',
            dataType: 'json',
            success: function( result ) {   
                $( droplists ).each(function() {                  
                    var selector = this.jqSelector;
                    var enable = false;         
                        $( selector ).empty().append( $( document.createElement('option') ).html( pleaseSelectTxt ).val( 0 ) ).attr('disabled',true);
                        
                        if (typeof(this)=='object' ) {
	                        $( result[ this.fillAllName ] ).each(function() {
	                            
	                            if( typeof this.timeZone != 'undefined' ) {
	                                
	                                $( selector ).append(
	                                        $( document.createElement('option') )
	                                            .html( this.name )
	                                            .attr('timeZone',this.timeZone)
	                                            .val( this.id )
	                                    ); 
	                                    enable = true;
	                                
	                            } else {
	                                
	                                $( selector ).append(
	                                        $( document.createElement('option') )
	                                            .html( this.name )
	                                            .val( this.id )
	                                    ); 
	                                    enable = true;                              
	                            }
	                            
	                        });  
                        }
                  
                        if( enable == true ) $( selector ).attr('disabled', false);
                        if( typeof result[ this.fillAllSelect ] != 'undefined' && result[ this.fillAllSelect ] != ''  ) {
                            $( selector ).val( result[ this.fillAllSelect ] ).find('option[value=0]').attr('disabled',true);                    
                        }                   
                });
            }
        });
    }

</script>

<script type="text/javascript" nonce="<tju:cspInlineNonce />">
    $(function() {
        $('fieldset.datetime').after(
            $( document.createElement('div') )
                .addClass('time-msg')
                .append( $( document.createElement('span') )  )
                .append( 
                    $( document.createElement('div') )
                        .addClass('time-msg-arrow')
                )
        );
        
        $('select[name=puHour], select[name=doHour], select[name=puMinute], select[name=doMinute]').change(function() {
            getHourDiff(
                $('select[name=puHour]').val(), 
                $('select[name=puMinute]').val(),
                $('select[name=doHour]').val(),
                $('select[name=doMinute]').val()
            );
        });
    });
    
    function getHourDiff(puHour, puMinute, doHour, doMinute) {      
        var puMinutes = -1;
        var doMinutes = -1;     
        try {
            puMinutes = (parseInt(puHour)*60) + parseInt(puMinute);
            doMinutes = (parseInt(doHour)*60) + parseInt(doMinute);
        } catch (e) {}
        $('.time-msg').hide();
        $('.time-msg span').html('');
        
        if(!isNaN(puMinutes)&&!isNaN(doMinutes)&&puMinutes!=-1&&doMinutes!=-1&&getPuDate().getTime()!=getDoDate().getTime()){
            var difference = doMinutes-puMinutes;
            if(difference>0&&difference<=60) {
                $('.time-msg span').html('<tju:javascriptescape>You can save a full days car rental price by reducing your rental duration by 1 hour</tju:javascriptescape>');
                $('.time-msg').show();
            } else if(difference>60&&difference<=120) {
                $('.time-msg span').html('<tju:javascriptescape>You can save a full days car rental price by reducing your rental duration by 2 hour</tju:javascriptescape>');
                $('.time-msg').show();
            } else if(difference>120&&difference<=180) {
                $('.time-msg span').html('<tju:javascriptescape>You can save a full days car rental price by reducing your rental duration by 3 hour</tju:javascriptescape>');
                $('.time-msg').show();
            }
        }       
    }

<script type="text/javascript" nonce="jlihcml4ukn80ab2ib4ackjug">
    /* UtmzUtils */
    (function() {

        var utmzCookieValues = null;

        function _getUtmzCookieValue() {
            var val = (document.cookie.match(/^(?:.*;)?\s__utmz=([^;]+)(?:.*)?$/)||[,null])[1];
            return val;
        }

        function _getUtmzCookieValues() {
            if (utmzCookieValues !== null) {
                return utmzCookieValues;
            }
            else {
                var utmzCookieValue = _getUtmzCookieValue();
                if (utmzCookieValue !== null) {
                    var pairs = utmzCookieValue.split('.').slice(4).join('.').split('|');
                    var ga = {};
                    for (var i = 0; i < pairs.length; i++) {
                        var temp = pairs[i].split('=');
                        ga[temp[0]] = temp[1];
                    }
                    utmzCookieValues = ga;
                    return utmzCookieValues;
                }
                else {
                    utmzCookieValues = {};
                    return utmzCookieValues;
                }
            }
        }

        function getValue(name) {
            var val = _getUtmzCookieValues()[name];
            return (typeof(val) !== 'undefined' ? val : '');
        }

        window.UtmzUtils = {
            getValue: getValue,
            _getUtmzCookieValue: _getUtmzCookieValue,
            _getUtmzCookieValues: _getUtmzCookieValues
        };

    })();
</script>

            window.getDevicePixelRatio = function () {
            var ratio = 1;
            // To account for zoom, change to use deviceXDPI instead of systemXDPI
            if (window.screen.systemXDPI !== undefined && window.screen.logicalXDPI !== undefined && window.screen.systemXDPI > window.screen.logicalXDPI) {
            // Only allow for values > 1
            ratio = window.screen.systemXDPI / window.screen.logicalXDPI;
            }
            else if (window.devicePixelRatio !== undefined) {
            ratio = window.devicePixelRatio;
            }
            return ratio;
            };

<script type="text/javascript" nonce="jlihcml4ukn80ab2ib4ackjug">
                function tagSrcIncludesPathSubstring(tag, substringTerms) {
                    var tagIncludesSubstring = false;
                    $.each(substringTerms, function(index, term) {
                        if (typeof tag.src != undefined && tag.src.indexOf(term) !== -1) {
                            tagIncludesSubstring = true;
                            return false; // breaks $.each loop
                        }
                    });

                    return tagIncludesSubstring;
                }

                function getGoogleMapCountFromTags(tags) {
                    var cnCountryOfResidence = false;
                    var googleMapUrls = cnCountryOfResidence ? ['maps.google.cn'] : ['maps.googleapis.com', 'maps.google.com'];

                    var googleMapCount = 0;
                    $.each(tags, function(index, tag) {
                        if (tagSrcIncludesPathSubstring(tag, googleMapUrls)) {
                            googleMapCount++;
                        }
                    });
                    return googleMapCount;
                }

                $(document).ready(function() {
                    var scriptTags = document.scripts;
                    var imgTags = document.images;

                    var googleMapCount = getGoogleMapCountFromTags(scriptTags);
                    var staticGoogleMapCount = getGoogleMapCountFromTags(imgTags);

                    GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'ErrorDebugInfo', 'GoogleMapScriptCount', 'PN:lp-default:'+googleMapCount, 1, true);
                    GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'ErrorDebugInfo', 'StaticGoogleMapImageCount', 'PN:lp-default:'+staticGoogleMapCount, 1, true);
                });

    	else

      3. Loosely Scoped Cookie (1)
        1. GET https://widget.rentalcars.com/
          Alert tags
          • WSTG-v42-SESS-02
          • OWASP_2021_A08
          • OWASP_2017_A06
          Alert description

          Cookies can be scoped by domain or path. This check is only concerned with domain scope.The domain scope applied to a cookie determines which domains can access it. For example, a cookie can be scoped strictly to a subdomain e.g. www.nottrusted.com, or loosely scoped to a parent domain e.g. nottrusted.com. In the latter case, any subdomain of nottrusted.com can access the cookie. Loosely scoped cookies are common in mega-applications like google.com and live.com. Cookies set from a subdomain like app.foo.bar are transmitted only to that domain by the browser. However, cookies scoped to a parent-level domain may be transmitted to the parent, or any subdomain of the parent.

					function GAQPushTransition(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction) {
						serialiseEvent(new GAQEvent(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction));
					}

					function GAQPushSecureTransition(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction,domain) {
						serialiseSecureEvent(new GAQEvent(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction),domain);
					}

					function GAQPush(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction) {
						pushEvent(new GAQEvent(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction));
					}

					function GAQPushPage(gaq_event_name, action){
						pushPageEvent(new GAQPageEvent(gaq_event_name, action));
					}

					function GAQPushLinkByPost(form) {
						try {
							pushLinkByPostEvent(new GAQLinkByPostEvent(form));
						} catch(err) {
						}
					}

					$(document).ready(function() {
						try {
							if ('/LoadingSearchResults.do' !== window.location.pathname) {
								$(deserialiseEvents(true)).each(function() {
									pushEvent(this);
								});
							}
						} catch (err) {

					var cookie_name = 'gaw_track';

					var accountPrefixes = new Array();
					accountPrefixes.push('m');

					function serialiseEvent(gaq_event) {
						var eventList = deserialiseEvents(false);
						if (!isDuplicateGAEvent(eventList, gaq_event)) {
							eventList.push(gaq_event);
						}
						if ('' === 'true' && '' === 'true') {
							$.cookies.set(cookie_name, $.toJSON(eventList));
						}
					}

					function serialiseSecureEvent(gaq_event,domain) {
						ajaxSetCookie({
							name: cookie_name,
							value: $.toJSON(gaq_event),
							domain: domain
						});
					}

					function deserialiseEvents(deleteAfterRead) {
						var events = new Array();

						if ($.cookies.get(cookie_name) !== null) {
							var json = $.evalJSON($.toJSON($.cookies.get(cookie_name)));

							if (json instanceof Array) {
								$(json).each(function() {
									events.push(new GAQEvent(this.gaq_event_name, this.category, this.action, this.label, this.value, this.non_interaction));
								});
							}
							else {
								events.push(new GAQEvent(json.gaq_event_name, json.category, json.action, json.label, json.value, json.non_interaction));
							}
						}

						if (deleteAfterRead) {
							$.cookies.set(cookie_name, null);
						}

						return events;
					}

					function pushEvent(event) {
						try{
							_gaq.push([event.gaq_event_name, event.category, event.action, event.label, event.value, event.non_interaction]);
							for (var i = 0; i < accountPrefixes.length; i++) {
								var prefix = accountPrefixes[i];
								_gaq.push([prefix + '.' + event.gaq_event_name, event.category, event.action, event.label, event.value, event.non_interaction]);
							}
						} catch(error){
							window.console.error('Could not push to Google Analytics because: \n', error);
						}
					}

					function pushPageEvent(e) {
						try{
							_gaq.push([e.gaq_event_name, e.action]);
							for (var i = 0; i < accountPrefixes.length; i++) {
								var prefix = accountPrefixes[i];
								_gaq.push([prefix + '.' + e.gaq_event_name, e.action]);
							}
						}catch(err){

						}
					}

					function pushLinkByPostEvent(e) {
						_gaq.push([e.gaq_event_name, e.form]);
						for (var i = 0; i < accountPrefixes.length; i++) {
							var prefix = accountPrefixes[i];
							_gaq.push([prefix + '.' + e.gaq_event_name, e.form]);
						}
					}


					/*
					 * Transition management
					 * Make sure duplicate events are not tracker on page transition
					 */
					function isDuplicateGAEvent(existingEvents, newEvent) {
						var key = newEvent.category + '#' + newEvent.action + '#' + newEvent.label;
						var found = false;
						for (var i = 0; i < existingEvents.length; i++) {
							var existingEventsKey = existingEvents[i].category + '#' + existingEvents[i].action + '#' + existingEvents[i].label;
							if (existingEventsKey === key) {
								found = true;
								break;
							}
						}
						return found;
					}


					/**
					 * Object representation of the Google Analytics _gaq.push(...) method
					 * https://developers.google.com/analytics/devguides/collection/gajs/eventTrackerGuide
					 */
					function GAQEvent(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction) {
						this.gaq_event_name = gaq_event_name;
						this.category = category;
						this.action = action;
						this.label = label;
						this.value = value;
						this.non_interaction = non_interaction;
					}

					function GAQPageEvent(gaq_event_name, action) {
						this.gaq_event_name = gaq_event_name;
						this.action = action;
					}

					function GAQLinkByPostEvent(form) {
						this.gaq_event_name = '_linkByPost';
						this.form = form;
					}

                                           $('#alternative-languages a').bind('click',function(e){
                                               e.preventDefault();
                                               lcf['langCurrencyActionType'].value='language';

                                           });

<script type="text/javascript" nonce="jlihcml4ukn80ab2ib4ackjug">
       	function formSubmit()
		{
	    if( $('#show_return').attr('checked') == true ) {
            showReturnDropDown();
        }

		$('input[name=locationName]').val( $( droplists[2].jqSelector ).find('option:selected').html() );
        $('input[name=dropLocationName]').val( $( droplists[5].jqSelector ).find('option:selected').html() );
        
        if( $( droplists[2].jqSelector ).val() == -1 && $( droplists[5].jqSelector ).val() == -1 ) {
            
            if( $( droplists[0].jqSelector ).val() == $( droplists[3].jqSelector ).val() && $( droplists[1].jqSelector ).val() == $( droplists[4].jqSelector ).val() ) {
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=searchType]').val('allareasgeosearch');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=doFiltering]').val('true');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterTo]').val('20');
            } else {                          
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=searchType]').val('manytomanysearch');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=doFiltering]').val('true');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
                $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterTo]').val('20');
            }
    
        } else if(  $( droplists[2].jqSelector ).val() == -1 && $( droplists[5].jqSelector ).val() != -1 ) {
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=searchType]').val('manytoonesearch');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=doFiltering]').val('true');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterTo]').val('20');
        } else if(  $( droplists[2].jqSelector ).val() != -1 && $( droplists[5].jqSelector ).val() == -1 ) {
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=searchType]').val('onetomanysearch');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=doFiltering]').val('true');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterTo]').val('20');
        } else {
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=searchType]').val('');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=doFiltering]').val('false');
        	$('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
            $('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterTo]').val('1000');
        }
       

		if(validateSearchResultsForm( document.SearchResultsForm ) ) {			
			saveInput();
			$('form[name=SearchResultsForm]').append(
                    $( document.createElement('input') )
                        .attr('type','hidden')
                        .attr('name','fromLocChoose')
                        .val(true)
                );
			$('form[name=SearchResultsForm]').submit();      
		}else {
			return false;
		}
	}
	
	 function droplistPopulate( data, droplistJSON, callback ) {
        $.ajax({
            url: '/AjaxDroplists.do',
            data: data + '&wrapNonAirports=true',
            dataType: 'json',
            success: function( result ) {            
                $( droplists ).each( function() {                 
                    if( this.index >= droplistJSON.index ) {                  
                        var element = $( this.jqSelector ).empty().append( $( document.createElement('option') ).html( pleaseSelectTxt ).val( 0 ) );                                      
                    }
                    if( this.index != droplistJSON.index )
                        $( element ).attr('disabled',true);
                });
                
                $( result ).each(function() {                 
                    
                    if( typeof this.timeZone != 'undefined' ) {
                        
                        $( droplistJSON.jqSelector ).append( 
                                $( document.createElement('option') )
                                    .html( this.name )
                                    .attr('timeZone',this.timeZone)
                                    .val( this.id ) )
                                .attr('disabled',false);
                    } else {
                        
                        $( droplistJSON.jqSelector ).append( 
                                $( document.createElement('option') )
                                    .html( this.name )
                                    .val( this.id ) )
                                .attr('disabled',false);                      
                    }   
                });
                if( typeof callback != 'undefined' ) callback.call(); 
            }
        });
    }   
	
	function droplistPopulateWithData( data ) {
        $.ajax({
            url: '/AjaxDroplists.do',
            data: data + '&mode=fillAll&wrapNonAirports=true',
            dataType: 'json',
            success: function( result ) {   
                $( droplists ).each(function() {                  
                    var selector = this.jqSelector;
                    var enable = false;         
                        $( selector ).empty().append( $( document.createElement('option') ).html( pleaseSelectTxt ).val( 0 ) ).attr('disabled',true);
                        
                        if (typeof(this)=='object' ) {
	                        $( result[ this.fillAllName ] ).each(function() {
	                            
	                            if( typeof this.timeZone != 'undefined' ) {
	                                
	                                $( selector ).append(
	                                        $( document.createElement('option') )
	                                            .html( this.name )
	                                            .attr('timeZone',this.timeZone)
	                                            .val( this.id )
	                                    ); 
	                                    enable = true;
	                                
	                            } else {
	                                
	                                $( selector ).append(
	                                        $( document.createElement('option') )
	                                            .html( this.name )
	                                            .val( this.id )
	                                    ); 
	                                    enable = true;                              
	                            }
	                            
	                        });  
                        }
                  
                        if( enable == true ) $( selector ).attr('disabled', false);
                        if( typeof result[ this.fillAllSelect ] != 'undefined' && result[ this.fillAllSelect ] != ''  ) {
                            $( selector ).val( result[ this.fillAllSelect ] ).find('option[value=0]').attr('disabled',true);                    
                        }                   
                });
            }
        });
    }

</script>

<script type="text/javascript" nonce="<tju:cspInlineNonce />">
    $(function() {
        $('fieldset.datetime').after(
            $( document.createElement('div') )
                .addClass('time-msg')
                .append( $( document.createElement('span') )  )
                .append( 
                    $( document.createElement('div') )
                        .addClass('time-msg-arrow')
                )
        );
        
        $('select[name=puHour], select[name=doHour], select[name=puMinute], select[name=doMinute]').change(function() {
            getHourDiff(
                $('select[name=puHour]').val(), 
                $('select[name=puMinute]').val(),
                $('select[name=doHour]').val(),
                $('select[name=doMinute]').val()
            );
        });
    });
    
    function getHourDiff(puHour, puMinute, doHour, doMinute) {      
        var puMinutes = -1;
        var doMinutes = -1;     
        try {
            puMinutes = (parseInt(puHour)*60) + parseInt(puMinute);
            doMinutes = (parseInt(doHour)*60) + parseInt(doMinute);
        } catch (e) {}
        $('.time-msg').hide();
        $('.time-msg span').html('');
        
        if(!isNaN(puMinutes)&&!isNaN(doMinutes)&&puMinutes!=-1&&doMinutes!=-1&&getPuDate().getTime()!=getDoDate().getTime()){
            var difference = doMinutes-puMinutes;
            if(difference>0&&difference<=60) {
                $('.time-msg span').html('<tju:javascriptescape>You can save a full days car rental price by reducing your rental duration by 1 hour</tju:javascriptescape>');
                $('.time-msg').show();
            } else if(difference>60&&difference<=120) {
                $('.time-msg span').html('<tju:javascriptescape>You can save a full days car rental price by reducing your rental duration by 2 hour</tju:javascriptescape>');
                $('.time-msg').show();
            } else if(difference>120&&difference<=180) {
                $('.time-msg span').html('<tju:javascriptescape>You can save a full days car rental price by reducing your rental duration by 3 hour</tju:javascriptescape>');
                $('.time-msg').show();
            }
        }       
    }

<script type="text/javascript" nonce="jlihcml4ukn80ab2ib4ackjug">
    /* UtmzUtils */
    (function() {

        var utmzCookieValues = null;

        function _getUtmzCookieValue() {
            var val = (document.cookie.match(/^(?:.*;)?\s__utmz=([^;]+)(?:.*)?$/)||[,null])[1];
            return val;
        }

        function _getUtmzCookieValues() {
            if (utmzCookieValues !== null) {
                return utmzCookieValues;
            }
            else {
                var utmzCookieValue = _getUtmzCookieValue();
                if (utmzCookieValue !== null) {
                    var pairs = utmzCookieValue.split('.').slice(4).join('.').split('|');
                    var ga = {};
                    for (var i = 0; i < pairs.length; i++) {
                        var temp = pairs[i].split('=');
                        ga[temp[0]] = temp[1];
                    }
                    utmzCookieValues = ga;
                    return utmzCookieValues;
                }
                else {
                    utmzCookieValues = {};
                    return utmzCookieValues;
                }
            }
        }

        function getValue(name) {
            var val = _getUtmzCookieValues()[name];
            return (typeof(val) !== 'undefined' ? val : '');
        }

        window.UtmzUtils = {
            getValue: getValue,
            _getUtmzCookieValue: _getUtmzCookieValue,
            _getUtmzCookieValues: _getUtmzCookieValues
        };

    })();
</script>

            window.getDevicePixelRatio = function () {
            var ratio = 1;
            // To account for zoom, change to use deviceXDPI instead of systemXDPI
            if (window.screen.systemXDPI !== undefined && window.screen.logicalXDPI !== undefined && window.screen.systemXDPI > window.screen.logicalXDPI) {
            // Only allow for values > 1
            ratio = window.screen.systemXDPI / window.screen.logicalXDPI;
            }
            else if (window.devicePixelRatio !== undefined) {
            ratio = window.devicePixelRatio;
            }
            return ratio;
            };

<script type="text/javascript" nonce="jlihcml4ukn80ab2ib4ackjug">
                function tagSrcIncludesPathSubstring(tag, substringTerms) {
                    var tagIncludesSubstring = false;
                    $.each(substringTerms, function(index, term) {
                        if (typeof tag.src != undefined && tag.src.indexOf(term) !== -1) {
                            tagIncludesSubstring = true;
                            return false; // breaks $.each loop
                        }
                    });

                    return tagIncludesSubstring;
                }

                function getGoogleMapCountFromTags(tags) {
                    var cnCountryOfResidence = false;
                    var googleMapUrls = cnCountryOfResidence ? ['maps.google.cn'] : ['maps.googleapis.com', 'maps.google.com'];

                    var googleMapCount = 0;
                    $.each(tags, function(index, tag) {
                        if (tagSrcIncludesPathSubstring(tag, googleMapUrls)) {
                            googleMapCount++;
                        }
                    });
                    return googleMapCount;
                }

                $(document).ready(function() {
                    var scriptTags = document.scripts;
                    var imgTags = document.images;

                    var googleMapCount = getGoogleMapCountFromTags(scriptTags);
                    var staticGoogleMapCount = getGoogleMapCountFromTags(imgTags);

                    GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'ErrorDebugInfo', 'GoogleMapScriptCount', 'PN:lp-default:'+googleMapCount, 1, true);
                    GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'ErrorDebugInfo', 'StaticGoogleMapImageCount', 'PN:lp-default:'+staticGoogleMapCount, 1, true);
                });

        group = $.cookies.get('group');

    	random = Math.floor(Math.random() * 3);
    	
    	if (random == 0)
    		group = 'A'
    	else if (random == 1)
    		group = 'B'
    	else
    		group = 'C';

					function GAQPushTransition(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction) {
						serialiseEvent(new GAQEvent(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction));

					function GAQPushSecureTransition(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction,domain) {

					function GAQPush(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction) {
						pushEvent(new GAQEvent(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction));
					}

					function GAQPushPage(gaq_event_name, action){
						pushPageEvent(new GAQPageEvent(gaq_event_name, action));
					}

					$(document).ready(function() {
						try {
							if ('/LoadingSearchResults.do' !== window.location.pathname) {

					var cookie_name = 'gaw_track';

					var accountPrefixes = new Array();
					accountPrefixes.push('m');

					function serialiseEvent(gaq_event) {
						var eventList = deserialiseEvents(false);
						if (!isDuplicateGAEvent(eventList, gaq_event)) {
							eventList.push(gaq_event);
						}
						if ('' === 'true' && '' === 'true') {
							$.cookies.set(cookie_name, $.toJSON(eventList));
						}
					}

					function serialiseSecureEvent(gaq_event,domain) {
						ajaxSetCookie({
							name: cookie_name,
							value: $.toJSON(gaq_event),
							domain: domain
						});
					}

					function deserialiseEvents(deleteAfterRead) {
						var events = new Array();

						if ($.cookies.get(cookie_name) !== null) {
							var json = $.evalJSON($.toJSON($.cookies.get(cookie_name)));

							if (json instanceof Array) {
								$(json).each(function() {
									events.push(new GAQEvent(this.gaq_event_name, this.category, this.action, this.label, this.value, this.non_interaction));
								});
							}
							else {
								events.push(new GAQEvent(json.gaq_event_name, json.category, json.action, json.label, json.value, json.non_interaction));
							}
						}

						if (deleteAfterRead) {
							$.cookies.set(cookie_name, null);
						}

						return events;
					}

					function pushEvent(event) {
						try{
							_gaq.push([event.gaq_event_name, event.category, event.action, event.label, event.value, event.non_interaction]);
							for (var i = 0; i < accountPrefixes.length; i++) {
								var prefix = accountPrefixes[i];
								_gaq.push([prefix + '.' + event.gaq_event_name, event.category, event.action, event.label, event.value, event.non_interaction]);
							}
						} catch(error){
							window.console.error('Could not push to Google Analytics because: \n', error);
						}
					}

					function pushPageEvent(e) {
						try{
							_gaq.push([e.gaq_event_name, e.action]);
							for (var i = 0; i < accountPrefixes.length; i++) {
								var prefix = accountPrefixes[i];
								_gaq.push([prefix + '.' + e.gaq_event_name, e.action]);
							}
						}catch(err){

						}
					}

					function pushLinkByPostEvent(e) {
						_gaq.push([e.gaq_event_name, e.form]);
						for (var i = 0; i < accountPrefixes.length; i++) {
							var prefix = accountPrefixes[i];
							_gaq.push([prefix + '.' + e.gaq_event_name, e.form]);
						}
					}


					/*
					 * Transition management
					 * Make sure duplicate events are not tracker on page transition
					 */
					function isDuplicateGAEvent(existingEvents, newEvent) {
						var key = newEvent.category + '#' + newEvent.action + '#' + newEvent.label;
						var found = false;
						for (var i = 0; i < existingEvents.length; i++) {
							var existingEventsKey = existingEvents[i].category + '#' + existingEvents[i].action + '#' + existingEvents[i].label;
							if (existingEventsKey === key) {
								found = true;
								break;
							}
						}
						return found;
					}


					/**
					 * Object representation of the Google Analytics _gaq.push(...) method
					 * https://developers.google.com/analytics/devguides/collection/gajs/eventTrackerGuide
					 */
					function GAQEvent(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction) {
						this.gaq_event_name = gaq_event_name;
						this.category = category;
						this.action = action;
						this.label = label;
						this.value = value;
						this.non_interaction = non_interaction;
					}

					function GAQPageEvent(gaq_event_name, action) {
						this.gaq_event_name = gaq_event_name;
						this.action = action;
					}

					function GAQLinkByPostEvent(form) {
						this.gaq_event_name = '_linkByPost';
						this.form = form;
					}

<script type="text/javascript" nonce="l0f8oj46d8f0586rvnf7984bif">
	$(document).ready(function(){
	    $('.drop_panel').hide();
	     
        $(".header_select_curr,.header_select_lang,.header_select_login").click(function() {
       
	        if($(this).next(".drop_panel").is(':visible')){ 
	        	$(this).next(".drop_panel").hide(); 
	        }
	        else { 
	            $(".drop_panel").hide(); 
	            $(this).next(".drop_panel").toggle(); 
	        }
	        return false; 
        });
        $(document).click(function() { 
            $(".drop_panel").hide(); 
        });
        $('.drop_panel').click(function(e) { 
        	e.stopPropagation(); 
	    });
	});
	
	function clearText(field) {
	    if (field.defaultValue == field.value) field.value = '';
	    else if (field.value == '') field.value = field.defaultValue;
	}
	
</script>

	        $(document).ready(function() {
	        	//document.getElementById('forgotten-box').style.display='none';
	         $('.forgotten a').click(function() {
	        	 	document.getElementById('email-box').style.display='block';
	        	 	if(document.getElementById('not-found') != null) {
	        	 		document.getElementById('not-found').style.display='none';
	        	 	}
	        	 	if(document.getElementById('sent') != null) {
	        	 		document.getElementById('sent').style.display='none';

	         $('#forgotSubmitInline').click(function() {
	        	 $.ajax({ 
	                 type: "GET",
					 url: '/ForgotBooking.do;jsessionid=A82DF3E23B13A4395B33DB1C09D48149.node528a',
	                 data: ({
	               		email:$('#forgotEmail').val()	        	 
	                 }),
	                 cache: false, 
	                 success: function(res) {
	                 	if(res.indexOf('true') != -1){
		                 	document.getElementById('email-box').style.display='none';
		                 	document.getElementById('sent').style.display='block';
							document.getElementById('not-found').style.display='none';
	                 	}else {
							document.getElementById('email-box').style.display='none';
							document.getElementById('sent').style.display='none';
							document.getElementById('not-found').style.display='block';
	                 	}
	                 },
	                 error: function(xhr, ajaxOptions, thrownError) {
						document.getElementById('email-box').style.display='none';
						document.getElementById('sent').style.display='none';
						document.getElementById('not-found').style.display='block';
	                 }
	                 
	        	 });
	         });
	        });
	        
	        
	        function showForgottenBox(show)
			{
				
				$('#forgotten-box').lightbox_me({centered: true, overlayCSS: {background: '#fff', opacity: 0.8}});  
				
				if(show) {
					document.getElementById('email-box').style.display='block';
					document.getElementById('not-found').style.display='none';
				}else {
					document.getElementById('email-box').style.display='none';
					document.getElementById('sent').style.display='none';
				}

			}

	$(function() {
    	$('#section-nav .section-nav-link').click(function() {
      		if (location.pathname.replace(/^\//,'') == this.pathname.replace(/^\//,'') && location.hostname == this.hostname) {
        		var target = $(this.hash);
        		target = target.length ? target : $('[name=' + this.hash.slice(1) +']');
        		if (target.length) {
          			$('html, body').animate({
            			scrollTop: target.offset().top
          			}, 1000);
          			return false;
        		}
      		}
    	});
  	});

<h2 class="h3 panel-heading border-box">Who we are</h2>
<div class="panel-body border-box">
<p class="lede">Our founders had the simple idea of wanting to make renting cars much better. And we’ve flourished because our customers love how we work.</p>
<p>We started in 2004 as TravelJigsaw. Four years later, we were making 1000 bookings a day. In 2010, we joined the Priceline Group and rebranded as Rentalcars.com.</p>
<p>Fast forward to today and we’re making 8 million bookings a year (and counting) in over 60,000 locations across 160 countries.</p>
<p>Our amazing growth relies on our fantastic, diverse team. Based in Manchester, our 1,200 colleagues hail from 65 nations: we&rsquo;ve succeeded because we cater to everyone, whatever their gender, nationality, language or culture. Check out our <a href="https://www.rentalcars.com/en/downloads/gender-pay.pdf">Gender Pay Gap report</a></p>

<div class="panel panel-default" id="holding-statement">
<h2 class="h3 panel-heading border-box">EU Digital Services Act</h2>
<div class="panel-body border-box">
<p>In accordance with Rentalcars.com’s obligations under the EU’s Digital Services Act, we estimate that the average monthly recipients* of the Rentalcars.com service in the European Union from 1 February 2023 up to and including 31 July 2023, is well below 45 million.</p>
<p>This is only an estimate and is based on the data available to Rentalcars.com at this time, and the limited guidance in the Digital Services Act (“DSA”). This estimate is required to be published under the DSA and should not be used for any other purpose. The methodologies used to estimate average monthly recipients as defined in the DSA require significant judgement and design inputs, are subject to data and other limitations, and inherently are subject to statistical variances and uncertainties. This estimate may be revised upwards or downwards as Rentalcars.com refines its approach and in response to the publication of methodology by the European Commission. As required by the DSA, we expect to publish a new estimate later in 2023.</p>
<p>Please refer to the <a target="_blank" href="https://ir.bookingholdings.com/overview/default.aspx">Booking Holdings Inc. Investor Relations</a> website for user metrics we consider relevant to Rentalcars.com’s business.</p>
<p>* ‘recipient of service’ is defined under the DSA to mean “any natural or legal person who uses an intermediary service, in particular for the purposes of seeking information and making it accessible”. This requires counting users to whom information was displayed by the Booking.com service, even if that user did not make a transaction.'</p>

<!--[if lte IE 9]>
	<script nonce="l0f8oj46d8f0586rvnf7984bif">
		$(document).ready(function(){

			var importedStyleSheets = $('link[href*=css]').length;
			var totalStyleSheets = $('style').length + importedStyleSheets;
			var IELimit = 31;

			if(totalStyleSheets >= IELimit) {
				mergeStyleSheetsOverLimit(IELimit);
			}

			/**
			Merges any style sheets after the 31st into the 31st one to fix the [IE style sheet limit]{@link https://support.microsoft.com/en-gb/help/262161/a-webpage-that-uses-css-styles-does-not-render-correctly-in-internet-explorer}.

			@description IE 7,8 and 9 limits the number of style sheets it renders to 31.
			In order to overcome the limitation, the function merges all the missed stylesheets
			(i.e any after the 31st) and places them into the 31st. Once this is done, it forces IE
	 		to render the styles again.
			The precondition is that the imported (e.g. <link> tags) style sheets are loaded
			before the inline ones.

			@todo The long term fix is to decrease this number with a build tool.
			*/
			function mergeStyleSheetsOverLimit(maximumAllowedStyleSheets) {

				var lastRenderedStyleSheetIndex = maximumAllowedStyleSheets - importedStyleSheets - 1;

				var concatenatedStyles = '';
				$('style').each(function(index, currentStyleSheet){
					// If the style has been ignored.
					if(index >= lastRenderedStyleSheetIndex) {
						concatenatedStyles += currentStyleSheet.innerHTML;
					}
				});

				var styleProperty = $('style').eq(lastRenderedStyleSheetIndex).prop('styleSheet');

				// The cssText property can only be set in older versions of IE.
				if(styleProperty !== undefined && styleProperty.cssText !== undefined) {
					// Set the css text property to force IE to render the styles again.
					// Details at https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/ms533698(v=vs.85).aspx.
					$('style').eq(lastRenderedStyleSheetIndex).prop('styleSheet').cssText = concatenatedStyles;
				}
			}

		});
	</script>
	<![endif]-->
